%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kejriwal%20to%20vacate%20CM%20residence%2C%20give%20up%20security%20to%20live%20as%20'common%20man'%3A%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726661825000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113460639%2Cimgsize-1647482.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-vacate-cm-residence-give-up-security-to-live-as-common-man-aap%2Farticleshow%2F113460039.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20outgoing%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20has%20announced%20he%20will%20give%20up%20all%20government%20facilities%20and%20vacate%20his%20official%20residence%20within%2015%20days.%20He%20aims%20to%20live%20like%20a%20common%20man%20without%20security%20or%20official%20vehicles.%20Concerns%20for%20his%20safety%20have%20been%20raised%20due%20to%20past%20attacks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fisker%20backtracks%20on%20telling%20owners%20to%20pay%20for%20repairs%20of%20malfunctioning%20EVs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fisker%20Ocean%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaac4ace3009a0fac71eca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fisker%20Ocean%20currently%20has%20five%20outstanding%20recalls.%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFisker%20has%20backtracked%20on%20telling%20owners%20of%20its%20EVs%20to%20pay%20for%20recall%20repairs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bankrupt%20EV%20firm%20previously%20said%20customers%20would%20have%20to%20cover%20the%20%26quot%3Blabor%20costs%26quot%3B%20of%20two%20outstanding%20recalls%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20Fisker%20Ocean%20owners%20previously%20told%20BI%20they%20had%20spent%20as%20much%20as%20%2470%2C000%20on%20cars%20that%20are%20now%20undrivable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOwners%20of%20Fisker%20Ocean%20EVs%20will%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ev-ocean-owners-pay-for-recall-repairs-bankruptcy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecall%20repairs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bankrupt%20auto%20company%20has%20changed%20a%20post%20on%20its%20website%20to%20say%20it%20will%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20repairs%20for%20two%20outstanding%20recalls%2C%20after%20initially%20saying%20owners%20of%20its%20Ocean%20EV%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20%26quot%3Blabor%20costs%26quot%3B%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20(NHTSA)%2C%20automakers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhtsa.gov%2Fsites%2Fnhtsa.gov%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2Fmvdefectsandrecalls_808795.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegally%20required%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20provide%20safety%20recall%20repairs%20free%20of%20charge%20for%20vehicles%20less%20than%2015%20years%20old.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20NHTSA%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Bis%20working%20to%20ensure%20vehicle%20owners%20receive%20recall%20remedies%20without%20charge%2C%20as%20required%20by%20federal%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f6cab01-3167-4ce2-9588-d4a632911209%5C%22%3EAn%20expensive%20'lawn%20ornament'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20previously%20reported%20that%20some%20customers%20who%20had%20paid%20as%20much%20as%20%2470%2C000%20for%20their%20Oceans%20had%20been%20left%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-owners-describe-chaos-to-keep-cars-running-after-bankruptcy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundrivable%20and%20unfixable%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20Fisker's%20bankruptcy%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20owner%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20battery%20problem%20had%20left%20his%20Ocean%20unusable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20literally%20a%20lawn%20ornament%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fisker%20Ocean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhtsa.gov%2Fvehicle%2F2023%2FFISKER%2FOCEAN%23recalls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrently%20has%20five%20outstanding%20recalls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20two%20%E2%80%94%20concerning%20the%20car's%20door%20handles%20and%20its%20water%20pump%20%E2%80%94%20requiring%20physical%20inspection%20and%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fiskerinc.com%2Frecalls%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR36gEwyTRnTBwX0oyZgOlM_tJdjixr1dLQNDIWwbskuI95PEZvtG22MNtU_aem_MHVp_9xGAO3goYBNqViD2Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecall%20FAQ%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20posted%20to%20Fisker's%20website%2C%20the%20bankrupt%20EV%20firm%20said%20that%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20financial%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20could%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-ev-ocean-owners-pay-for-recall-repairs-bankruptcy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecover%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20necessary%20parts%20for%20those%20recalls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20the%20repairs%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recall%20FAQ%20also%20stated%20that%20any%20%26quot%3Blabor%20costs%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20repairs%20would%20need%20to%20be%20covered%20by%20vehicle%20owners.%20Fisker%20apologized%20for%20%26quot%3Bany%20inconvenience%20this%20may%20cause.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20early%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20recall%20FAQ%20had%20been%20updated%20to%20state%20that%20Fisker%20would%20%26quot%3Bprovide%20the%20necessary%20parts%20(including%20the%20labor)%20at%20no%20cost%26quot%3B%20to%20Ocean%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reversal%20will%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20long-suffering%20Fisker%20Ocean%20owners%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20previously%20told%20BI%20they%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-owners-describe-chaos-to-keep-cars-running-after-bankruptcy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%20to%20contact%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20find%20repair%20shops%20that%20could%20fix%20their%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20owner%20Steven%20Hammer%20told%20BI%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20to%20pay%20for%20recall%20repairs%20was%20%26quot%3Bpositively%20infuriating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20one%20more%20punch%20to%20the%20gut%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Colorado%20resident%2C%20who%20previously%20had%20to%20pay%20to%20transport%20his%20Ocean%20to%20a%20dealership%20in%20another%20state%20to%20fix%20a%20broken%20roof%20panel%20after%20being%20unable%20to%20reach%20anyone%20at%20Fisker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20level%20of%20cost%20cutting%20and%20incompetence%20that's%20hard%20to%20bear.%20We%20paid%20BMW%20prices%20and%20got%20Yugo%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20Hammer%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Yugoslavian%20hatchback%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F06%2F10%2Fbusiness%2Fyugo-cars.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecame%20notorious%20for%20its%20unreliability%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20released%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recall%20FAQ%2C%20Fisker%20said%20it%20would%20address%20the%20other%20three%20recalls%20on%20the%20Ocean%20with%20a%20software%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20warned%20customers%20to%20drive%20their%20vehicles%20%26quot%3Bwith%20caution%26quot%3B%20until%20the%20recalls%20have%20been%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20is%20the%20second%20failed%20auto%20company%20founded%20by%20famed%20former%20Tesla%20designer%20Henrik%20Fisker.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-automotive-files-for-bankruptcy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollapsed%20into%20bankruptcy%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EV%20startup%20struggled%20to%20ship%20cars%20and%20address%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmkbhd-fisker-ocean-review-marques-brownlee-video-tiktok-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equality%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20electric%20cars%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happened-henrik-fisker-automotive-startup-ocean-electric-vehicle-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20and%20current%20employees%20telling%20BI%20mismanagement%20and%20cost%20cutting%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20partly%20to%20blame%20for%20its%20demise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisker%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Fisker%20or%20own%20an%20Ocean%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atcarter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Etcarter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-backtracks-says-it-will-cover-recall-repair-costs-ocean-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726661642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaad5cd17aa3c7b2b3a1bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-backtracks-says-it-will-cover-recall-repair-costs-ocean-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20failed%20auto%20company%20changed%20a%20post%20on%20its%20website%20this%20week%20to%20say%20it%20would%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20repairs%20for%20two%20outstanding%20recalls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter