0expands%20its%20network%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-ev-chargers-look-like-gas-stations-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20charging%20stations%20with%20EVgo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier%20in%20September%2C%20the%20companies%20announced%20they%20are%20working%20together%20on%20a%20network%20of%20fast-charging%20hubs%20that%20will%20look%20and%20operate%20like%20gas%20stations%20(minus%20the%20gas).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20back-to-back%20charging%20announcements%20from%20GM%20should%20signal%20to%20customers%20that%20the%20Detroit%20car%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20improving%20the%20public%20charging%20experience%2C%20said%20GM%20Energy%20Vice%20President%20Wade%20Sheffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20intent%20to%20be%20the%20leader%20in%20providing%20fast%2C%20convenient%2C%20and%20safe%20charging%20in%20the%20public%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheffer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb4e0e8a-ed18-4c61-a275-f9d027c4619c%5C%22%3ECar%20companies%20working%20together%20is%20rare%20%E2%80%94%20but%20necessary%20for%20EV%20charging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGM%20was%20among%20the%20many%20car%20companies%20that%20partnered%20with%20Tesla%20last%20year%20to%20adopt%20the%20North%20American%20Charging%20Standard%20(NCAS).%20Crosstown%20rival%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-to-bring-supercharger-network-to-rival-ford-musk-says-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFord%20was%20the%20first%20to%20join%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20NCAS%20in%20May%202023%2C%20and%20companies%20like%20GM%2C%20Rivian%2C%20Volvo%2C%20and%20BMW%20later%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdoption%20has%20been%20slow%2C%20however%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-recruiter-wants-to-hire-interns-impacted-by-tesla-cuts-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20shrank%20its%20Supercharger%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%20GM%20is%20only%20the%20third%20company%20to%20gain%20access%20after%20Ford%20and%20Rivian%20drivers%20started%20using%20Superchargers%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20patch%20holes%20in%20the%20US%20charging%20infrastructure%20have%20been%20haphazard%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-charging-range-improving-americans-still-dont-want-electric-cars-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20public%20charging%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20longer%20drives%20has%20long%20been%20a%20pain%20point%20for%20electric%20vehicle%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20rapid%20improvements%2C%20with%20the%20number%20of%20charging%20stations%20in%20the%20US%20more%20than%20doubling%20since%202020%20and%20%247.5%20billion%20in%20promised%20federal%20funding%20for%20500%2C000%20new%20EV%20stations%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20though%2C%20Sheffer%20says%20otherwise%20aggressive%20competitors%20will%20have%20to%20work%20together%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-range-ev-charging-station-infrastructure-issues-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolve%20the%20charging%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20there%20is%20fierce%20competition%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20our%20vehicles%2C%20we%20can%20all%20align%20on%20wanting%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20charger%20experience%20for%20our%20customers%20collectively%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheffer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgm-chevy-tesla-supercharger-ev-charging-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726660861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9d03ace3009a0fac6f862%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b