%3EThe%20world's%20biggest%20food%20company%20is%20going%20small%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENestl%C3%A9%20is%20launching%20new%20frozen%20meals%20designed%20for%20busy%20Americans%20who%20just%20aren't%20that%20hungry%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20or%20who%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20losing%20some%20weight%20via%20portion%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENestl%C3%A9's%20newest%20product%20line%20%26quot%3BVital%20Pursuit%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20slate%20of%20low-calorie%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-meal-plan-weight-fat-loss-nutritionist-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-protein%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20relatively%20cheap%20and%20easy%20on-the-go%20foods%20for%20people%20on%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20Mounjaro%2C%20and%20Zepbound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vital%20pursuit%20meals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea0397cfb7f307e5728ac3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EVital%20Pursuit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meals%20cost%20less%20than%20%245%20and%20are%20available%20at%20retailers%20including%20Target%20and%20Walmart%2C%20starting%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20don't%20%3Cem%3Eexplicitly%3C%2Fem%3E%20say%20it%20on%20the%20box%2C%20but%20Nestl%C3%A9%20told%20Business%20Insider%20these%20new%20products%20were%20designed%20for%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20people%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20typically%20consume%20around%201%2C200%20to%201%2C800%20calories%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20GLP-1%20users%20suddenly%20discover%20they%20don't%20have%20as%20much%20%26quot%3Bfood%20noise%26quot%3B%20or%20constant%20thoughts%20about%20eating%20anymore.%20They%20also%20may%20feel%20full%20very%20quickly%2C%20and%20experience%20slower%20digestion%20than%20others.%20These%20small%20meals%2C%20branded%20as%20protein-rich%2C%20are%20designed%20to%20help%20GLP-1%20users%20lose%20more%20fat%2C%20and%20less%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristen%20Stoehr%2C%20a%20registered%20dietician%20and%20the%20Vital%20Pursuit%20brand%20manager%20at%20Nestl%C3%A9%2C%20says%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20GLP-1%20user%20to%20eat%20these%20foods.%20After%20all%2C%20only%20about%206%25%20of%20Americans%20are%20actually%20on%20a%20GLP-1%20drug%20right%20now%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20health%20policy%20research%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kff.org%2Fhealth-costs%2Fpoll-finding%2Fkff-health-tracking-poll-may-2024-the-publics-use-and-views-of-glp-1-drugs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKFF%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20a%20brand%20for%20those%2082%25%20of%20Americans%20who%20are%20managing%20their%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoehr%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referencing%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20two%20of%20the%20new%20meals%20before%20their%20release%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20though%20I%20was%20skeptical%2C%20I%20have%20to%20say%20they%20tasted%20better%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20were%20clearly%20designed%20to%20keep%20me%20full%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Ewhile%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Nestl%C3%A9%20brought%20new%20processed%20foods%20to%20the%20frozen%20aisle%20was%20about%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-keto-what-is-ketosis-keto-diet-explained-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eketo%20diets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20plant-based%20meals%20were%20trending%2C%20Stoehr%20said.%20The%20new%20meals%20are%20leaning%20into%20some%20fresher%2C%20newer%20nutrition%20trends%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20high%20protein%2C%20with%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgluten-free-diet-unhealthy-most-people-without-celiac-disease-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egluten-free%3C%2Fa%3E%20options%2C%20and%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20fiber%20in%20each%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20always%20tweaking%20our%20lineup%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20relevant%20for%20today's%20consumer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegistered%20dietician%20Alix%20Turoff%20and%20nutrition%20coach%20Mike%20Molloy%2C%20both%20independent%20nutrition%20experts%20who%20don't%20work%20at%20Nestl%C3%A9%2C%20took%20a%20look%20at%20the%20nutrition%20facts%20and%20components%20in%20the%20meals%20for%20Business%20Insider.%20Their%20reviews%2C%20like%20my%20taste%20test%2C%20were%20relatively%20positive%2C%20but%20not%20glowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d53e8495-0b13-4acf-91a0-35a77cbeb699%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20380-calorie%20mini%20pizza%20with%2026%25%20of%20the%20daily%20protein%20recommendation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cooked%20pizza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea0397cfb7f307e5728ac0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHilary%20Brueck%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20frozen%20pizza%20the%20flavor%20on%20this%20little%20item%20was%20decent%2C%20with%20a%20nice%20tangy%20sauce.%20While%20gluten-free%2C%20cauliflower%20crusts%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20chewy%20or%20crumbly%2C%20this%20had%20a%20crunchy%20crust.%20It%20wasn't%20on%20par%20with%20actual%20pizza%2C%20but%20it%20was%20just%20as%20good%20as%20any%20other%20microwaveable%20option%20I've%20had.%20The%20pepperoni%20was%20my%20least%20favorite%20part.%20It%20tasted%20rubbery%2C%20thick%2C%20and%20didn't%20have%20much%20flavor.%20It%20could%20never%20compete%20with%20the%20perfectly%20greasy%2C%20crunchy%2C%20spicy%20cup%20pepperoni%20on%20most%20New%20York%20pizza%20pies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuroff%20says%20this%20meal%20is%20a%20bit%20high%20in%20saturated%20fat%20for%20her%20liking%20(7%20grams%2C%2035%25%20DV)%20but%20she%20was%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20sodium%20content%20(930mg%2C%2040%25%20DV)%20%E2%80%94%20often%20a%20concern%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-making-ultra-processed-foods-healthier-in-major-new-study-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultra-processed%20convenience%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20meal%20could%20use%20a%20little%20more%20fiber%2C%20so%20she%20would%20recommend%20eating%20it%20with%20some%20veggies%20or%20a%20side%20salad.%20The%20protein%20dose%2C%20at%2022%20grams%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bsolid%26quot%3B%20but%20not%20high%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20someone%20trying%20to%20lose%20weight%20without%20GLP-1's%2C%20I'd%20actually%20recommend%20aiming%20for%20more%20like%2030%2B%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20meal%20for%20satiety%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%20Though%20it%20isn't%20the%20most%20nutritious%2C%20wholesome%20meal%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Turoff%20said%20it%20was%20important%20to%20consider%20what%20it%20might%20actually%20be%20replacing%20in%20someone's%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20likely%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20healthier%20choice%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20convenience%20foods%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20a%20meal%20like%20this%20can%20be%20a%20practical%2C%20balanced%20option%20for%20someone%20trying%20to%20manage%20their%20weight%20or%20make%20healthier%20choices%20compared%20to%20what%20they%20might%20otherwise%20grab%20on%20a%20busy%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalloy%20said%20people%20should%20practice%20the%2080%2F20%20rule%20here%3A%20if%20they're%20getting%2080%25%20of%20their%20diet%20from%20whole%2C%20fresh%20foods%20like%20whole%20grains%2C%20veggies%2C%20and%20protein%20sources%20including%20eggs%2C%20seafood%2C%20and%20chicken%2C%20then%20he's%20OK%20with%20the%20extra%2020%25%20of%20their%20diet%20being%20things%20like%20these%20ultra-processed%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20my%20pizza%20for%20lunch%20and%20was%20satisfied%20until%20after%20dinnertime%2C%20without%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b7dc2d8-2f0e-412a-889c-43349ba6e59c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20340-calorie%20grilled%20chicken%20bowl%20with%2022%20grams%20of%20protein%20was%20an%20OK%20desk%20lunch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chicken%20in%20microwave%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea0397ce3009a0fac7164e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHilary%20Brueck%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20garlic%20herb%20grilled%20chicken%20bowl%20wasn't%20half%20bad%20either%2C%20though%20it%20did%20leave%20me%20a%20bit%20hungrier%20than%20the%20pizza.%20I%20liked%20the%20herby%20and%20just%20slightly%20creamy%20flavor%2C%20which%20after%20a%20quick%20glance%20at%20the%20ingredient%20panel%20I%20chalked%20up%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20some%20Parmesan%20cheese%2C%20basil%2C%20garlic%2C%20lemon%20juice%2C%20and%20feta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sauce%20wasn't%20heavy%2C%20and%20paired%20well%20with%20the%20coin-sized%20pieces%20of%20chicken%20(small!)%2C%20brown%20rice%2C%20carrots%2C%20and%20broccoli.%20Turoff%20was%20more%20impressed%20with%20the%20ingredient%20list%20here%2C%20and%20said%20the%20sodium%20(640mg%2C%2028%25%20DV)%20and%20vitamin%20A%20(70%25%20DV)%20stats%20were%20better%20than%20the%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20independent%20nutrition%20professionals%20we%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20said%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20options%20out%20there%20for%20weight%20loss%20and%20portion%20control.%20It's%20not%20like%20Nestl%C3%A9%20suddenly%20reinvented%20the%20convenience%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20meals%20seem%20like%20a%20decent%20option...%20but%20not%20a%20great%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Malloy%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20the%20focus%20on%20upping%20protein%20is%20important%20for%20people%20on%20GLP-1%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20one%20thing%20I%20think%20is%20contributing%20to%20the%20excessive%20muscle%20mass%20loss%20that%20people%20are%20experiencing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20helps%20them%20to%20get%20more%20protein%20overall%2C%20that's%20a%20win%20in%20my%20book.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuroff%20was%20also%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20on%20GLP-1s%20may%20not%20have%20much%20of%20an%20appetite%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20motivated%20to%20cook%20or%20prepare%20their%20own%20food%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20convenient%2C%20portion-controlled%20frozen%20meals%20like%20these%20can%20be%20really%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20products%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20useful%20tool%20for%20those%20who%20may%20not%20yet%20feel%20comfortable%20in%20the%20kitchen%20or%20who%20struggle%20to%20maintain%20a%20consistent%20routine%20of%20preparing%20balanced%20meals.%20For%20someone%20on%20GLP-1%20medications%2C%20who%20might%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20appetite%20changes%20or%20simply%20trying%20to%20adjust%20to%20their%20new%20eating%20patterns%2C%20having%20a%20frozen%20meal%20that%20is%20quick%20and%20easy%20to%20prepare%20can%20reduce%20decision%20fatigue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cooked%20chicken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea0397cfb7f307e5728ac2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHilary%20Brueck%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20not%20the%20target%20audience%20for%20these%20meals%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20have%20this%20chicken%20and%20rice%20on%20hand%20during%20a%20busy%20day%20at%20the%20office%2C%20and%20ready%20in%20under%20five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22665e06c1-bdc0-4601-b2de-6d1ddcc1375e%5C%22%3ENestl%C3%A9%20is%20bracing%20for%20a%20drop%20in%20appetite%20for%20fast-food%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20Nestl%C3%A9's%20first%20foray%20into%20the%20growing%20business%20of%20catering%20to%20GLP-1%20users%20across%20the%20US.%20For%20several%20months%20now%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nestle.com%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fhealth-science-glp-1-nutrition-support-platform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20has%20been%20selling%3C%2Fa%3E%20protein%20powders%2C%20shakes%2C%20supplements%2C%20electrolytes%20and%20other%20nutrition%20products%20geared%20towards%20GLP-1%20weight%20loss%20on%20a%20dedicated%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20call%20with%20BI%2C%20Nestl%C3%A9's%20senior%20manager%20for%20health%20and%20wellness%2C%20Marlene%20Schmidt%2C%20cited%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.morganstanley.com%2Fideas%2Fobesity-drugs-food-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicting%20that%20by%202035%2C%20roughly%207%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%20will%20be%20on%20a%20weight%20loss%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20same%20report%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said%20that%20consumption%20of%20sodas%2C%20baked%20goods%2C%20and%20salty%20snacks%20%26quot%3Bmay%20fall%20up%20to%203%25%20by%202035.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20biggest%20food%20giant%20in%20the%20world%20wants%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20ready%20for%20that%20consumer%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnestle-new-microwave-weight-loss-meals-for-ozempic-diet-review-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726660802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea0400ce3009a0fac7166e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnestle-new-microwave-weight-loss-meals-for-ozempic-diet-review-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20biggest%20food%20company%20is%20targeting%20Ozempic%20users%20with%20small%2C%20protein-packed%20meals%20for%20under%20%245.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnestle-new-microwave-weight-loss-meals-for-ozempic-diet-review-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Practical%3A%2015%20Opposition%20Parties%20Rubbish%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFifteen%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20opposed%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20proposal%2C%20which%20was%20green-lighted%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20today.%20The%20proposal%2C%20part%20of%20the%20report%20of%20a%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20has%20been%20adopted%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20the%20media%20after%20the%20cabinet%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20the%20plan%20is%20not%20pragmatic%20or%20practical.%20Party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20elections%20come%2C%20they%20(the%20BJP)%20are%20not%20getting%20any%20issues%20to%20raise.%20So%20they%20divert%20attention%20from%20real%20issues.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20while%20releasing%20its%20manifesto%20for%20next%20month's%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%2C%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20is%20just%20BJP%20tactics%20to%20divert%20attention.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20against%20the%20Constitution%2C%20this%20is%20contrary%20to%20democracy%2C%20this%20is%20against%20federalism.%20The%20country%20will%20never%20accept%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20oppose%20the%20idea%20of%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%2C%26quot%3Bsaid%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal's%20Manoj%20Jha.%20%26quot%3BAshwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%20said%20that%2080%20per%20cent%20people%20supported%20it%20during%20the%20consultation.%20We%20want%20to%20know%20who%20the%2080%20per%20cent%20people%20are.%20Did%20anyone%20ask%20us%20anything%20or%20talk%20to%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20plan%2C%20which%20proposes%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20NDA%20and%20many%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Under%20it%2C%20urban%20body%20and%20panchayat%20polls%20have%20to%20be%20held%20within%20100%20days%20of%20the%20general%20and%20state%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20implementing%20it%20would%20require%20two-third%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%20since%20it%20involves%20amendment%20of%20the%20constitution.%20At%20least%20six%20amendments%20would%20be%20required%20to%20bring%20it%20into%20effect.%20After%20this%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20ratified%20by%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20NDA%20has%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20getting%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20either%20house%20could%20prove%20a%20challenge.%20Of%20the%20245%20seats%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20112%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2085.%20For%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20at%20least%20164%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20292%20of%20545%20seats.%20The%20two-thirds%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%20364.%C2%A0%20But%20the%20situation%20could%20be%20dynamic%2C%20since%20the%20majority%20would%20be%20counted%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20members%20present%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20that%20have%20traditionally%20given%20issue-based%20support%20have%20a%20handful%20of%20MPs%20too%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20known%20which%20side%20they%20will%20be%20on%20now.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20had%20supported%20the%20ides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20have%20been%20routed%20in%20the%20elections%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Andhra%20Prsdeh%20--%20one%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20other%20by%20BJP%20ally%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%207%20MPs%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20YSRCP%209%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20four%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20AIADMK%20has%20only%20four%20MPs%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20clearing%20all%20the%20hurdles%2C%20the%20law%20can%20be%20put%20in%20place.%20But%20the%20government%2C%20in%20the%20meantime%20also%20has%20to%20create%20bipartisan%20support%20and%20a%C2%A0%20countrywide%20narrative.%20Its%20implementation%20can%20only%20be%20done%20after%202029%2C%20the%20Kovind%20report%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20earlier%20pitches%20for%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20have%20fallen%20through%20after%20the%20opposition%20refused%20to%20back%20the%20idea%2C%20contending%20that%20it%20was%20anti-democratic%2C%20against%20the%20Constitution%20and%20impractical.%20The%20CPM%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20replace%20parliamentary%20democracy%20by%20slipping%20in%20a%20Presidential%20form%20of%20government%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20the%20back-door%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20an%20enthusiastic%20votary%20of%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20idea%2C%20had%20said%20this%20was%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20debate%2C%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bneed%20for%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20held%20at%20different%20places%20every%20few%20months.%20The%20effect%20it%20has%20on%20development%20work%20is%20known%20to%20all.%20This%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20studied%20and%20presiding%20officers%20can%20be%20guiding%20force%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726660740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgbga996o_mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_12_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-pragmatic-or-practical-15-opposition-parties-rubbish-one-nation-one-election-plan-6593247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fifteen%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20opposed%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20which%20was%20green-lighted%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-pragmatic-or-practical-15-opposition-parties-rubbish-one-nation-one-election-plan-6593247%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20after%20more%20Iranian%20and%20North%20Korean%20missiles%20to%20help%20it%20tip%20the%20balance%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20experts%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Putin%20at%20a%20long%20table%20talking%20to%20Iran's%20leader%20while%20Shoigu%20looks%20in%20a%20folder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaa6eecfb7f307e572920d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22