0is%20to%20be%20believed.%20A%20statement%20was%20expected%20at%2011.30%20am%20but%20there%20was%20no%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20did%20say%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20had%20consultations%20with%20senior%20party%20figures%2C%20and%20that%20a%20formal%20notification%20may%20be%20released%20this%20evening%2C%20from%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20over%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20promotion%20has%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months%3B%20in%20August%20senior%20party%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20party%20is%20considering%20the%20step%20as%20part%20of%20prepping%20for%20the%202026%20Assembly%20election%20and%20to%20strengthen%20its%20second-rung%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20son%20led%20the%20DMK's%20campaign%20for%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20and%20the%20dominant%20showing%20-%20the%20party-led%20alliance%20won%20all%2039%20seats%20-%20has%20added%20to%20the%20clamour%20for%20his%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20party's%20successful%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%20and%20the%202021%20Assembly%20election%2C%20in%20which%20the%20party%20swept%20133%20of%20the%20state's%20234%20seats%20and%20dumped%20rivals%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(and%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20answer%20to%20some%20(within%20the%20party)%20who%20thought%20Udhayanidhi%20lacks%20the%20experience%20and%20political%20acumen%20to%20command%20acceptance%20from%20the%20party's%20veteran%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20sources%20also%20said%20the%20promotion%20for%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counter%20the%20entry%20of%20Tamil%20actor%20Vijay%20into%20politics.%20The%20hugely%20popular%20actor%20-%20whose%20legions%20of%20fans%20have%20named%20him%20'%3Cem%3Ethalapathy%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20'commander'%20-%20launched%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Tamilaga%20Vettri%20Kazhagam%2C%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20however%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20talk%20of%20his%20elevation%2C%20saying%20that%20only%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20could%20take%20that%20decision.%20He%20did%2C%20though%2C%20say%20%26quot%3Bsome%20leaders...%20want%20me%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20too%20he%20underplayed%20talk%20of%20becoming%20his%20father's%20deputy%2C%20declaring%20%26quot%3Ball%20ministers%20in%20our%20government%20are%20'deputy%20chief%20ministers'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20expected%20promotion%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20fired%20(a%20predictable)%20volley%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20has%20slammed%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20possible%20elevation%20as%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B.%20The%20party%20also%20referred%20to%20ex%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20Karunanidhi%20-%20MK%20Stalin's%20father%20and%20Udhayanidhi's%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20spokesperson%20Kovai%20Sathyan%20also%20declared%20that%20naming%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20%26quot%3Bsignal%20the%20end%20of%20the%20DMK%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20party%20will%20split%20ahead%20of%20the%202026%20election...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20also%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20before%20the%202021%20election%2C%20had%20said%20neither%20his%20son%20nor%20son-in-law%20(daughter%20Senthamarai%20Stalin's%20husband%2C%20Sabareesan)%20would%20enter%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20sources%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%2C%20pointing%20out%20Udhayanidhi%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bdemocratically%20elected%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20MLA.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20(then)%20is%20the%20question%20of%20dynasty%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20