0One%20Election'%20Is%20Our%20Commitment%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20making%20this%20a%20reality%20will%20require%20two-third%20of%20Parliament%20to%20side%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20since%20the%20proposed%20system%20involves%20amending%20-%20in%20at%20least%20six%20places%20-%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20has%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20but%20is%20short%20of%20that%20two-thirds%20mark%20-%20by%2052%20votes%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%2072%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20ratified%20by%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Panel%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20simultaneous%20poll%20will%20%26quot%3Btransform%20the%20electoral%20process%20(and)%20governance%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Boptimise%20scarce%20resources%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20high-profile%20panel%20said%2C%20noting%2032%20parties%20and%20prominent%20judicial%20figures%2C%20including%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20Chief%20Justices%20and%20High%20Court%20judges%2C%20had%20backed%20this%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20advantages%20listed%20for%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20are%20that%20it%20makes%20the%20electoral%20process%20easier%20for%20voters.%20Synchronising%20polls%20will%20also%20result%20in%20higher%20and%20faster%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20therefore%20a%20more%20stable%20economy%2C%20the%20panel%20argued%2C%20claiming%20a%20single%20round%20of%20elections%20will%20allow%20businesses%20and%20corporate%20firms%20to%20take%20decisions%20without%20fear%20of%20adverse%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20has%20also%20reasoned%20that%20(eventually)%20holding%20elections%20at%20all%20three%20levels%20-%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20for%20state%20Assemblies%2C%20and%20for%20panchayats%20-%20will%20%26q