tv-yuva-anurag-thakur-makes-strong-case-for-one-nation-one-election-see-details-5326223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIf%20some%20state%20elections%20are%20advanced%20or%20kept%20on%20hold%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2010-15%20polls%20can%20be%20held%20together...%20If%20we%20save%20this%20money%20India%20won't%20have%20to%20wait%20for%202047%2C%20but%20will%20achieve%20its%20'%3Cem%3EViksit%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(developed%20India)%20dreams%20much%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20before%20the%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind-led%20panel%20was%20announced%2C%20the%20Law%20Minister%20outlined%20the%20government's%20rationale%20and%20told%20Parliament%20simultaneous%20elections%20represent%20financial%20savings%20as%20it%20cuts%20down%20on%20multiple%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces%2C%20and%20also%20helps%20political%20parties%20save%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Opposition%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%2015%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20opposed%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20this%20proposal%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20pragmatic%20and%20practical%26quot%3B.%20Party%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20while%20releasing%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20for%20next%20month's%20Haryana%20election%2C%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20going%20to%20succeed...%20the%20people%20will%20not%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-pragmatic-or-practical-15-opposition-parties-rubbish-one-nation-one-election-plan-6593247%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENot%20Practical%3A%2015%20Parties%20Rubbish%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20Plan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20elections%20come%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20issues%20to%20raise%2C%20they%20divert%20attention...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20said%C2%A0the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-leader-p-chidambaram-says-one-nation-one-election-not-possible-under-present-constitution-6576943%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20system%C2%A0is%20not%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20present%20Constitution%2C%20as%20it%20requires%20at%20least%20five%20constitutional%20amendments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20opposition%20parties%2C%20specifically%20those%20in%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20including%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20have%20also%20been%20critical%20of%20this%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20while%20releasing%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-lok-sabha-election-manifesto-uniform-civil-code-citizenship-for-tamils-neet-one-nation-one-election-caa-in-crosshairs-in-dmks-lok-sabha-manifesto-5274425%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu's%20DMK%20vowed%20to%20scrap%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20were%20to%20win%20the%20election.%20Two%20months%20earlier%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20called%20the%20proposal%20%26quot%3Ba%20design%20to%20subvert%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B(allow)%20autocracy%20(in)%20a%20democratic%20garb...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagainst-autocracy-mamata-banerjee-rejects-one-nation-one-election-4841508%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2