2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Pager%20Attacks%3A%20What%20Next%20For%20Hezbollah%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F3egae548_lebanon-hospital_625x300_18_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20could%20easily%20dismiss%20it%20as%20a%20spy%20film%20plot%20if%20it%20weren't%20so%20real%3A%20a%20highly%20sophisticated%20'pager%20attack'%20purportedly%20by%20Israeli%20agencies%20has%20left%20dozens%20dead%20and%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Gaza%20crisis.%20Nine%20people%20were%20reported%20killed%20and%20over%202%2C700%2C%20including%20civilians%2C%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20series%20of%20text%20pagers%20supposedly%20used%20by%20Hezbollah%20members%20exploded%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Iran's%20ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%2C%20Mojtaba%20Amani%2C%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20Israel%20had%20intercepted%20the%20group's%20supply%20chains%20and%20laced%20more%20than%205%2C000%20of%20these%20devices%20with%20explosives.%20A%20Taiwanese%20company%2C%20Gold%20Apollo%2C%20has%20denied%20charges%20that%20it%20was%20the%20provider%20of%20the%20consignment.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20February%2C%20Hezbollah%20chief%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20had%20warned%20his%20group%20against%20the%20use%20of%20mobile%20phones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Complexity%20To%20Deal%20With%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20officially%20taken%20credit%20for%20the%20attack.%20However%2C%20the%20incident%20adds%20one%20more%20layer%20to%20an%20intricate%20and%20clandestine%20face-off%20between%20Israeli%20agencies%20and%20the%20Lebanese%20militia%20group%20as%20both%20try%20to%20avoid%20a%20full-scale%20confrontation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intent%20behind%20such%20an%20audacious%20attack%20appears%20to%20be%20to%20inflict%20a%20psychological%20and%20strategic%20blow%20rather%20than%20a%20tactical%20one.%20The%20attack%20would%20be%20added%20to%20a%20not-too-long%20but%20notable%20list%20of%20Israeli%20operations%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20that%20have%20primarily%20been%20designed%20to%20highlight%20the%20state's%20intrusions%20within%20its%20enemy's%20infrastructure%2C%20whether%20political%2C%20military%2C%20or%20technological.%20Examples%20include%20the%20use%20of%20automated%20AI-assisted%20weapons%20to%20assassinate%20Iranian%20scientist%20Mohsen%20Fakhrizadeh%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Tehran%20in%202021%2C%20the%20elimination%20of%20Hamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20in%20central%20Tehran%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20and%20various%20other%20clandestine%20operations%20aimed%20at%20disrupting%20Iran's%20nuclear%20programme.%20The%20basic%20idea%20behind%20these%20operations%2C%20including%20ones%20now%20involving%20low-grade%20tech%20like%20pagers%2C%20is%20optics%2C%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Israeli%20state%20can%20target%20its%20detractors%20at%20the%20time%20and%20place%20of%20its%20choosing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%20has%20been%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20turning%20into%20a%20full%20conflict%20for%20months%20now.%20Recently%2C%20Israel%20flew%20fighter%20jets%20over%20Beirut%20just%20before%20a%20sermon%20by%20Nasrallah%2C%20to%20show%20force%20and%20awareness.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20eliminate%20his%20immediate%20deputies%2C%20such%20as%20Fuad%20Shukr.%20Recent%20reports%20have%20once%20again%20suggested%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20may%20look%20to%20remove%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%2C%20who%20has%20criticised%20the%20way%20decisions%20have%20been%20taken%20on%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Despite%20the%20political%20fault%20lines%20within%20Israel%20on%20these%20issues%20-%20including%20the%20far%20too%20public%20discrepancies%20between%20civil%20and%20military%20leaderships%20-%20there%20is%20a%20consensus%20to%20target%20both%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%20in%20order%20to%20secure%20long-term%20security%20narratives%2C%20which%20were%20deemed%20lost%20after%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Iran%20Intervene%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20the%20'Axis%20of%20Resistance'%2C%20Hezbollah%2C%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20remains%20strong%20compared%20to%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20its%20fighting%20strength%20deplete%20significantly%20in%20recent%20months.%20Also%2C%20in%20choosing%20not%20to%20join%20Hamas%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20October%202023%20attack%20in%20Israel%2C%20Hezbollah%20managed%20to%20buy%20some%20time.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20approach%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20two%20lines%20of%20thinking.%20First%2C%20direct%20aggression%20against%20Israel%20in%20the%20country's%20north%20would%20in%20all%20likelihood%20not%20only%20invite%20a%20response%20of%20Israeli%20air%20power%20but%20that%20of%20the%20US%20as%20well%2C%20causing%20mass%20casualties%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20for%20which%20Hezbollah%20would%20have%20to%20be%20answerable.%20Second%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20lack%20of%20clarity%20on%20whether%20Iran%20would%20directly%20intervene%20in%20support%20of%20the%20said%20axis.%20For%20instance%2C%20Tehran%20hasn't%20yet%20directly%20responded%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Haniyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20thus%20seemingly%20prefers%20a%20more%20protracted%20response%2C%20causing%20nuisance%20and%20displacement%20in%20Israel's%20north%20instead%20of%20going%20for%20a%20traditional%2C%20full-scale%20border%20conflict%20that%20it%20very%20well%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20the%20growing%20tensions%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20are%20threatening%20to%20jeopardise%20diplomatic%20tracks%20being%20promoted%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20US%20to%20put%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20place.%20Israeli%20hostages%20remain%20under%20Hamas%20captivity%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20in%20response%20are%20set%20to%20continue.%20Netanyahu%20has%20made%20no%20qualms%20in%20admitting%20that%20such%20warfare%20will%20prevail%20till%20Hamas%20is%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Psychological%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20both%20Hamas%20and%20Netanyahu%20have%2C%20in%20their%20own%20way%2C%20obstructed%20ceasefire%20efforts.%20A%20political%20settlement%20today%20will%20require%20a%20prolonged%20secession%20of%20hostilities.%20While%20Nasrallah%20claims%20that%20his%20group%20does%20not%20want%20total%20war%2C%20both%20sides%20are%20sliding%20towards%20tactical%20exchanges.%20But%20even%20these%20tactical%20attacks%20can%20very%20well%20lead%20to%20a%20broader%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20latest%20explosions%2C%20Hezbollah's%20'low-tech'%20pager%20communication%20network%20has%20already%20been%20busted%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20the%20group%20to%20operate%2C%20debate%2C%20and%20deploy%20forces.%20In%20the%20short%20term%2C%20if%20not%20tactically%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20managing%20to%20secure%20at%20least%20psychological%20victories%20against%20Hezbollah%20and%20its%20ilk.%20In%20the%20long%20term%2C%20things%20remain%20as%20uncertain%20as%20before.%20It%20won't%20be%20surprising%20if%20the%20Gaza%20crisis%20and%20accompanying%20regional%20tensions%20spill%20well%20into%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BKabir%20Taneja%20is%20a%20Fellow%20with%20the%20Strategic%20Studies%20Programme%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'The%20ISIS%20Peril%3A%20The%20World's%20Most%20Feared%20Terror%20Group%20and%20its%20Shad