%2F400X400%2F1709750255-5349.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faurobindo-to-acquire-remaining-49-stake-in-gls-pharma-for-rs-22-5-crore-124091800825_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20acquisition%20is%20undertaken%20to%20hold%20the%20entire%20ownership%20of%20GLS%20by%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20transaction%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20completed%20before%20December%2031%2C%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faurobindo-to-acquire-remaining-49-stake-in-gls-pharma-for-rs-22-5-crore-124091800825_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faurobindo-to-acquire-remaining-49-stake-in-gls-pharma-for-rs-22-5-crore-124091800825_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faurobindo-to-acquire-remaining-49-stake-in-gls-pharma-for-rs-22-5-crore-124091800825_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20Polls%20Good%20For%20Growth%2C%20Says%20BJP%3B%20Opposition%20Dubs%20It%20Cheap%20Stunt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20clearing%20the%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20committee%20report%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20Assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%20at%20the%20same%20time%20-%20known%20as%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20-%20has%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20how%20effective%20the%20proposal%20would%20actually%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2047%20political%20parties%20provided%20feedback%20on%20the%20proposal%20and%20while%2032%20said%20they%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20it%2C%2015%20opposed%20it%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20DMK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20has%20said%20that%20it%20would%20result%20in%20higher%20economic%20growth%20by%20providing%20stability%2C%20allow%20parties%20in%20power%20to%20focus%20on%20governance%2C%20improve%20policy%20making%2C%20and%20help%20voters%20and%20increase%20voter%20turnout%20by%20making%20casting%20the%20ballot%20easier%20and%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20times%20it%20will%20need%20to%20be%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20deemed%20the%20move%20impractical%20and%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20rejected%20by%20people%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20termed%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20stunt%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20that%20if%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20was%20something%20that%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20implement%20why%20were%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Maharashtra%20not%20announced%20with%20those%20for%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Could%20Work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProponents%20of%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20say%20that%20for%20India%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20unencumbered%20governance%20is%20very%20important%20and%20having%20elections%20every%20few%20months%20distracts%20the%20ruling%20party%20from%20focusing%20on%20the%20issues%20that%20matter%20by%20making%20them%20get%20into%20campaign%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20point%20has%20been%20highlighted%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20speaking%20about%20the%20need%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20since%20he%20assumed%20office%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202014.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20said%20the%20implementation%20of%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20which%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20is%20the%20party's%20commitment%20and%20the%20committee%20led%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20had%20received%20positive%20and%20innovative%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20is%20our%20commitment.%20We%20have%20talked%20about%20this%20in%20parliament%20as%20well.%20We%20have%20also%20formed%20a%20committee.%20The%20committee%20has%20also%20submitted%20its%20report.%20So%20in%20terms%20of%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20many%20people%20have%20come%20on%20board%20in%20the%20country.%20Many%20people%20have%20given%20their%20suggestions%20to%20the%20committee.%20The%20committee%20received%20very%20positive%20and%20innovative%20suggestions%20and%20the%20country%20will%20benefit%20a%20lot%20if%20we%20can%20implement%20this%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018%2C626-page%20report%20was%20submitted%20in%20March%20after%20extensive%20consultations%20with%20stakeholders%2C%20experts%20and%20research%20over%20191%20days%20since%20the%20committee%20was%20constituted%20on%20September%202%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20and%20parties%20that%20have%20supported%20simultaneous%20elections%20have%20said%20that%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20economic%20growth%20as%20it%20would%20provide%20policy%20stability%20and%20allow%20businesses%20to%20take%20decisions%20without%20fear%20of%20changes%20that%20could%20upset%20their%20roadmap.%20In%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20it%20would%20also%2C%20they%20say%2C%20avoid%20disruption%20of%20supply%20chains%20and%20production%20cycles%20which%20happen%20because%20of%20migrant%20workers%20remaining%20absent%20to%20cast%20their%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20governments%2C%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20can%20help%20them%20avoid%20policy%20paralysis%20and%20increase%20their%20focus%20on%20governance.%20Frequent%20elections%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20impact%20policy%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneous%20polls%20will%20also%20help%20voters%20by%20ensuring%20ease%20of%20casting%20ballots%20and%20avoiding%20the%20fatigue%20caused%20by%20frequent%20elections.%20Supporters%20of%20the%20move%20argue%20that%20it%20will%20also%20boost%20voter%20turnout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20approval%20of%20the%20proposal%20of%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20by%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20is%20historic.%20This%20will%20increase%20transparency%20in%20elections%20and%20reduce%20the%20financial%20burden%20on%20the%20government%20exchequer.%20I%20thank%20Honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Cabinet%20for%20this%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Vinod%20Tawde%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20May%20Not%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpponents%20argue%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20real%20risk%20of%20regional%20issues%20getting%20overshadowed%20by%20national%20ones%20when%20the%20entire%20country%20votes%20at%20once.%20It%20has%20already%20been%20seen%20that%20voters%20pick%20different%20parties%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20still%20different%20ones%20for%20municipal%20polls.%20Experts%20attribute%20this%20to%20problems%20in%20the%20region%2C%20as%20well%20as%20good%20work%20done%20by%20the%20party%20in%20power%20the%20state%20or%20local%20body%2C%20being%20in%20focus%20when%20Assembly%20or%20local%20body%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20federal%20structure%20gives%20a%20set%20of%20powers%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20and%20those%20who%20argue%20against%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20say%20they%20can%20erode%20the%20importance%20of%20state%20governments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20elections%20are%20also%20often%20seen%20as%20referendums%20on%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20when%20they%20happen%20at%20different%20times%2C%20voters%20can%20hold%20the%20ruling%20party%20accountable%20by%20signalling%20their%20dissatisfaction%20with%20it.%20Elections%20being%20held%20together%20in%20a%20gap%20of%20five%20years%2C%20some%20argue%2C%20deprives%20voters%20of%20that%20opportunity%20and%20there%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20of%20elected%20representatives%20becoming%20complacent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneous%20elections%20were%20held%20four%20times%2C%20in%201951-52%2C%201957%2C%201962%20and%201967%20but%20could%20not%20continue%20because%20of%20the%20premature%20dissolution%20of%20some%20state%20Assemblies%20in%201968%20and%201969.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20also%20dissolved%20prematurely%20in%201970%20and%20fresh%20elections%20were%20held%20in%201971.%20While%20proponents%20cite%20the%20initial%20simultaneous%20elections%20as%20proof%20that%20they%20can%20work%2C%20opponents%20argue%20that%20India%20had%20fewer%20states%20and%20a%20smaller%20population%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition's%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20the%20plan%20is%20not%20practical%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20voters%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Assembly%20election%20has%20begun%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Haryana%20on%20October%205.%20The%20Congress%20has%20also%20cited%20practical%20challenges%2C%20including%20amending%20the%20Constitution%20and%20cutting%20the%20terms%20of%20some%20Assemblies%20short%20to%20align%20them%20with%20the%20schedule%20of%20simultaneous%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20public.%20This%20is%20not%20going%20to%20succeed...%20the%20people%20will%20not%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20had%20said%20%26quot%3B'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20is%20not%20possible%20under%20the%20present%20Constitution.%20It%20requires%20at%20least%20five%20constitutional%20amendments.%20Mr%20Modi%20does%20not%20have%20the%20majority%20to%20put%20those%20constitutional%20amendments%20in%20either%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20Rajya%20Sabha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20%C2%A0Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20dismissed%20the%20move%20as%20a%20'jumla'%20(empty%20promise)%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20is%20just%20another%20cheap%20stunt%20from%20the%20anti-democratic%20BJP.%20%C2%A0Why%20were%20Maharashtra%20elections%20not%20announced%20along%20with%20elections%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3F%20Here's%20why.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20announced%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%20scheme%20in%20the%20budget%20this%20June.%20The%20first%20tranche%20reached%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20women%20in%20August%20and%20second%20tranche%20will%20reach%20beneficiaries%20in%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20do%20three%20states%20in%20one%20go%20and%20you%20talk%20about%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election.%20And%20also%20tell%20us%2C%20how%20many%20constitutional%20amendments%2C%20including%20curtailing%20or%20extending%20terms%20of%20state%20assemblies%2C%20will%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20simultaneous%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20India%20earlier%20and%20there%20was%20a%20reason%20it%20was%20stopped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20that%20be%20changed%20now%3F%20Elections%20will%20be%20held%20together%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20states...%20say%20no%20government%20can%20be%20formed%20in%20a%20state%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20or%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20will%20there%20be%20a%20proxy%20government%20with%20governor's%20rule%20or%20President's%20rule%20till%20the%20next%20election%20or%20will%20a%20fresh%20election%20be%20called%20for%20such%20states.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20fresh%20election%2C%20then%20the%20link%20breaks%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jha%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BMost%20importantly%2C%20after%20the%20BJP%20was%20reduced%20to%20240%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20we%20thought%20PM%20Modi%20would%20speak%20about%20issues%20related%20to%20employment.%20This%20is%20a%20diversionary%20tactic%2C%20nothing%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726658220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhtn21a9c_voting-generic_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-pros-and-cons-simultaneous-polls-good-for-growth-says-bjp-opposition-dubs-it-cheap-stunt-6593545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Cabinet%20clearing%20the%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20committee%20report%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%20at%20the%20same%20time%20-%20known%20as%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%20-%20has%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20how%20effective%20the%20proposal%20would%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-pros-and-cons-simultaneous-polls-good-for-growth-says-bjp-opposition-dubs-it-cheap-stunt-6593545%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20now%3F%20More%20questions%20than%20answers%20after%20pager%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726658160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-pager-gold-apollo-hezbollah_6689225.jpg%3F20240918115916%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.s