3Cp%3EYana%20Blajeva%2FMillennium%20Media%2FKetchup%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEthan%20Baird%2C%20a%20video%20game%20animator%20who%20runs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHellboyNews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHellboyNews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20character's%20biggest%20fan%20accounts%20on%20X%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20studio's%20half-hearted%20approach%20to%20marketing%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20opportunity%20because%20they%20have%20an%20IP%20on%20their%20hands%20which%20goes%20against%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryan-reynolds-deadpool-box-office-success-marvel-superhero-slump-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuperhero%20fatigue%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20low-budget%20horror%20film%2C%20which%20we%20don't%20really%20see%20in%20the%20genre%20anymore.%20It's%20so%20disappointing%20because%20the%202019%20movie%20was%20horrible%2C%20but%20they%20put%20so%20much%20effort%20into%20marketing%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20it's%20the%20complete%20opposite%3A%20No%20one%20knows%20that%20this%20film%20is%20coming%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%2C%20and%20the%20information%20vacuum%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20speculation%20and%20rumor.%20Some%20believe%20Millennium%20Media%20made%20%26quot%3BThe%20Crooked%20Man%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20small%20budget%20with%20the%20sole%20intention%20of%20keeping%20the%20rights%20to%20Hellboy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20probably%20made%20it%20to%20keep%20the%20rights%20because%20the%20film%20was%20made%20in%20just%20over%20a%20year%2C%20on%20a%20low%20budget%2C%20and%20that's%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20get%20a%20motion%20picture%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Baird%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20bad%20saying%20that%20because%20it's%20evident