20why%20%26quot%3Bwith%20platforms%2C%20like%20iTunes%2C%20you%20get%20better%20placing%20on%20the%20platform%20if%20you've%20had%20a%20theatrical%20release.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247839e56-1267-49e8-8a9c-83b3ee5b43e3%5C%22%3EThe%20director%20of%20'Hellboy%3A%20The%20Crooked%20Man'%20said%20he%20knew%20the%20movie%20would%20face%20'challenges'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20man%20with%20shaved%20horns%20and%20black%20sideburns%20in%20a%20coat%20stands%20next%20to%20a%20woman%20with%20dark%20hair%20and%20a%20jacket%2C%20she%20has%20a%20cut%20on%20her%20cheek.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e43538bf0250c21493269b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJack%20Kesy%20as%20Hellboy%20and%20Adeline%20Rudolph%20as%20Bobbie%20Jo%20Song.%3Cp%3EYana%20Blajeva%2FMillennium%20Media%2FKetchup%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20delay%20between%20filming%20wrapping%20up%20and%20the%20trailer%20dropping%2C%20Taylor%20told%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20longer%20than%20it%20should%20have%2C%20but%20I've%20just%20got%20to%20be%20really%20generic%20and%20say%2C%20every%20movie%20has%20its%20challenges.%20And%20I%20was%20aware%20going%20into%20it%20that%20there%20would%20be%20certain%20challenges%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20disappointed.%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20didn't%20elaborate%20on%20why%20he%20expected%20to%20face%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20also%C2%A0noted%20that%20movies%2C%20in%20general%2C%20are%20hard%20to%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20just%20all%20hard.%20A%20lot%20of%20times%20things%20take%20longer%20than%20they%20should.%20We%20didn't%20have%20as%20much%20time%20as%20we%20should%20before%20we%20started%20and%20then%20ended%20up%20having%20way%20too%20much%20time%20after%20we%20finished.%20I%20wish%20we%20could%20have%20reversed%20those%20two%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20added%20that%20his%20team%20was%20well-prepared%20for%20shooting%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20tight%20production%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20exactly%20what%20we%20were%20doing.%20We%20had%20a%20really%20tight%20shooting%20schedule%20and%20were%20really%20aggressive.%20We%20were%20doing%2030%2C%2040%20setups%20a%20day%2C%20and%20we%20really%20kicked%20ass%20getting%20this%20movie%20done.%20And%20in%20post-production%2C%20we%20knew%20exactly%20what%20we%20wanted.%20We%20had%20this%20thing%20assembled%20very%2C%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%20Media%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20shown%20Taylor's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20filmmaking%20point%20of%20view%2C%20post%20was%20really%20easy.%20From%20a%20business%20point%20of%20view%2C%20post%20was%20challenging.%20It%20was%20just%20tough.%20But%20thankfully%2C%20it's%20over%20and%20we%20finally%20got%20it%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhellboy-the-crooked-man-new-movie-release-date-marketing-why-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726657153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e44b67bf0250c214933142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhellboy-the-crooked-man-new-movie-release-date-marketing-why-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHellboy%3A%20The%20Crooked%20Man%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20latest%20reboot%20of%20the%20beloved%20character%2C%20but%20a%20messy%20marketing%20campaign%20means%20only%20hardcore%20fans%20know%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.com%20(Eammon%20Jacobs)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhellboy-the-crooked-man-new-movie-release-date-marketing-why-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22