Bruckheimer%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20thin%20line%20between%20plagiarism%20and%20inspiration.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20chat%20with%20ETimes%20he%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20filmmakers%20around%20the%20world%20being%20'inspired'%20by%20his%20billion-dollar%20franchises%20like%20'Tom%20Gun'%20and%20'Pirates%20of%20the%20Caribbean'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Karen%20Pereira%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yogi%20Adityanath%20Turns%20To%20Shayari%20To%20Target%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20today%20turned%20to%20'shayari'%20to%20target%20Opposition%20parties%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20and%20also%20termed%20them%20%26quot%3BBhasmasur%26quot%3B%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20using%20the%20power%20of%20the%20people%20to%20suppress%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20before%202014%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20before%202017%2C%20the%20sights%20they%20have%20shown%20to%20the%20country...%20they%20make%20tall%20claims%20now%2C%20but%20if%20you%20start%20looking%20at%20their%20dark%20deeds%2C%20they%20will%20realise...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20reminded%20of%20a%20poet's%20words.%20Nazar%20nahin%20hai%2C%20nazaron%20ki%20baat%20karte%20hain%2C%20zameen%20par%20chand-sitaron%20ki%20baat%20karte%20hain%2C%20woh%20haath%20jodkar%20basti%20ko%20lutne%20wale%2C%20bhari%20sabha%20mein%20sudharon%20ki%20baat%20karte%20hain%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Ghaziabad.%20The%20lines%20roughly%20translate%20to%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20have%20eyes%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20sights%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20moon%20and%20stars%20on%20earth%2C%20they%20loot%20with%20folded%20hands%20and%20then%20talk%20about%20reforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20duo%20has%20come%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20mislead.%20They%20have%20only%20looted%2C%20they%20have%20done%20good%20to%20no%20one%20apart%20from%20their%20families.%20Whenever%20the%20people%20have%20given%20them%20power%2C%20they%20have%20misused%20it%20like%20Bhasmasur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhasmasur%20is%20a%20mythological%20character%20who%20was%20granted%20a%20unique%20power%20by%20Lord%20Shiva%20--%20anyone%20whose%20head%20Bhasmasur%20placed%20his%20hand%20on%20turned%20to%20ash.%20The%20demon%20misused%20this%20power%20and%20became%20a%20terror.%20Lord%20Vishnu%20then%20assumed%20the%20appearance%20of%20Mohini%2C%20a%20danseuse%2C%20who%20charmed%20Bhasmasur%20into%20a%20dance.%20During%20the%20dance%2C%20he%20placed%20his%20hand%20on%20his%20head%20and%20turned%20to%20ash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20target%20your%20faith%20with%20the%20power%20you%20have%20given%20them.%20If%20the%20Congress%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20was%20bringing%20laws%20to%20suppress%20Hindus%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20was%20following%20them%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adityanath%20accused%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20bowing%20to%20mafia%20and%20notorious%20criminals%20during%20its%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BThey%20call%20religious%20leaders%20mafia.%20Aurangzeb's%20soul%20has%20entered%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20responding%20to%20Mr%20Yadav's%20remarks%20in%20which%20he%20said%20there%20is%20not%20much%20difference%20between%20a%20mathadheesh%20(head%20of%20a%20math)%20and%20mafia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adityanath%20said%20Hindus%20had%20to%20flee%20the%20state%20during%20the%20Samajwadi%20party's%20rule%20and%20daughters%20were%20in%20danger.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20daughters%20are%20safe%2C%20trad