m.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsbi-raises-rs-7-500-crore-through-issuance-basel-iii-compliant-bonds-124091800775_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsbi-raises-rs-7-500-crore-through-issuance-basel-iii-compliant-bonds-124091800775_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%203%20policy%20issues%20portfolio%20managers%20are%20most%20concerned%20about%20this%20election%20season%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20including%20one%20that%20wasn't%20discussed%20during%20the%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(Composite%20image)%20Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cd4e701aa2ac29ee347b3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%3Cp%3EIan%20Maule%2FGetty%20Images%2C%20ANDREW%20CABALLERO-REYNOLDS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20at%20stake%20this%20presidential%20election%2C%20which%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20close%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20issues%20of%20taxes%2C%20tariffs%2C%20and%20the%20possible%20elimination%20of%20the%20filibuster.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlthough%20not%20mentioned%20at%20the%20debate%2C%20removing%20the%20filibuster%20could%20have%20major%20implications%20for%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Wall%20Street%2C%20policy%20%E2%80%94%20not%20politics%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20motto%20leading%20up%20to%20November.%20And%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20policy%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20don't%20agree%20on%20much%20of%20anything%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20key%20areas%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20shake%20up%20markets%20more%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20strategists%20at%20DWS%20Asset%20Management%20identified%20three%20hot-button%20issues%20that%20portfolio%20managers%20are%20most%20concerned%20about%20this%20election%20cycle%3A%20taxes%2C%20tariffs%2C%20and%20the%20possible%20elimination%20of%20the%20filibuster.%20Taxes%20and%20tariffs%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20of%20national%20attention%2C%20but%20the%20filibuster%20situation%20has%20not%20%E2%80%94%20and%20DWS%20thinks%20investors%20should%20be%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abc5ce97-4713-426f-8786-cc41087396af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeath%20and%20taxes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20tax%20policy%20is%20at%20the%20top%20of%20money%20managers'%20minds%2C%20according%20to%20Frank%20Kelly%2C%20senior%20political%20strategist%20at%20DWS.%20Wall%20Street%20is%20looking%20towards%20Trump%20to%20be%20the%20more%20business-friendly%20candidate%20on%20a%20tax%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tax%20Cut%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20(TCJA)%20is%20up%20for%20renewal%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20and%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20have%20different%20plans%20for%20what'll%20happen%20next.%20Trump%20is%20looking%20to%20renew%20the%20existing%20TCJA%2C%20while%20Harris%20has%20promised%20to%20rewrite%20the%20tax%20code%20and%20raise%20the%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20to%2028%25%20from%20its%20current%2021%25.%20That%20would%20deliver%20a%207%25%20hit%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20earnings%20per%20share%2C%20and%20the%20statutory%20tax%20impact%20on%20a%20corporation%20could%20range%20from%205%20to%2010%25%20depending%20on%20the%20company's%20geography%20mix%2C%20according%20to%20David%20Bianco%2C%20DWS%20Americas%20chief%20investment%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20corporate%20tax%20rate%2C%20Wall%20Street%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20Harris'%20proposal%20for%20a%20financial%20transactions%20tax%20that%20would%20apply%20to%20all%20stock%2C%20bond%2C%20and%20derivative%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224caf2777-8d3e-4a7e-99c7-399716b113a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20Wall%20Street%20is%20monitoring%20is%20tariffs.%20If%20elected%2C%20Trump%20has%20promised%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20of%20up%20to%2020%25%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBianco%20thinks%20such%20a%20policy%20would%20harm%20the%20economy.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20dangerous%20to%20really%20double%20down%20on%20some%20policies%20like%20the%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Such%20dramatic%20tariffs%20could%20lead%20to%20consumers%20paying%20more%20for%20goods%2C%20as%20well%20as%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20from%20other%20countries.%20According%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20tariffs%20could%20put%20inflationary%20pressures%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20hinder%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unlike%20tax%20policy%2C%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20voted%20on%20by%20Congress%2C%20tariffs%20are%20much%20easier%20to%20implement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20are%20something%20the%20executive%20president%20can%20do%20with%20executive%20authority%20to%20a%20great%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20Bianco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20if%20Trump%20were%20elected%2C%20he%20could%20quickly%20move%20to%20make%20high%20tariffs%20become%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d24e1ecf-6627-48c0-a22a-abd2e1391003%5C%22%3EThe%20filibuster%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20under-the-radar%20issue%20keeping%20portfolio%20managers%20up%20at%20night%3A%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20filibuster%2C%20according%20to%20Kelly's%20conversations%20with%20clients.%20This%20topic%20wasn't%20mentioned%20at%20the%20debate%2C%20but%20it%20could%20have%20big%20implications%20for%20all%20types%20of%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20especially%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20have%20been%20proponents%20of%20eliminating%20the%20filibuster%2C%20and%20Kelly%20believes%20a%20Harris%20win%20could%20further%20incentivize%20this%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20analysts%20expect%20a%20very%20close%20election%2C%20and%20even%20a%20minute%20change%20could%20be%20enough%20to%20push%20the%20needle%20on%20the%20outcome%20for%20either%20candidate.%20The%20races%20for%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%20are%20contentious%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20Monica%20Guerra%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20Wealth%20Management's%20head%20of%20US%20policy.%20That%20means%20a%20single-party%20sweep%20is%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20out%20of%20the%20question%20for%20the%20Democrats%20to%20retain%20the%20Senate%2C%20it%20would%20be%20highly%20unlikely%20for%20them%20to%20win%20the%2060%20seats%20necessary%20to%20override%20a%20filibuster%2C%20Kelly%20said.%20Eliminating%20the%20filibuster%20would%20be%20a%20way%20for%20Democrats%20to%20pass%20legislation%20quicker%2C%20such%20as%20Harris'%20tax%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Ablin%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Cresset%20Capital%20Management%2C%20summarized%20the%20situation%20aptly%3A%20%26quot%3BInvestors%20celebrate%20gridlock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGridlock%20prevents%20extensive%20policy%20changes%20and%2C%20subsequently%2C%20market%20volatility.%20Guerra's%20research%20shows%20that%20equity%20markets%20perform%20the%20best%20under%20split%20control%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20how%20important%20gridlock%20is%20to%20the%20market%2C%20there's%20not%20enough%20conversation%20around%20the%20impacts%20of%20eliminating%20the%20filibuster%2C%20Kelly%20believes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemocrats%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seeing%20a%20president-elect%20Harris%20stymied%20in%20the%20first%20two%20years%20in%20any%20number%20of%20legislative%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20a%20policy%20like%20this%20could%20gain%20ample%20support%20from%20voters%20who%20feel%20frustrated%20that%20Washington%2