%20and%20later%20became%20a%20boat%20pilot.%20When%20he%20had%20to%20take%20medical%20retirement%20because%20of%20an%20injury%2C%20he%20got%20involved%20with%20international%20maritime%20organizations.%20He%20loved%20the%20work.%20I%20think%20his%20eventual%20retirement%20contributed%20to%20his%20death%20two%20years%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20know%20my%20choice%20isn't%20for%20everyone.%20My%20in-laws%20are%20both%20approaching%2090%2C%20and%20they've%20been%20retired%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades.%20They%20loved%20that%20they%20don't%20%26quot%3Bhave%20to%26quot%3B%20do%20anything%20%E2%80%94%20they%20just%20do%20what%20they%20want.%20Yet%20when%20I%20look%20at%20their%20choices%2C%20I%20know%20I%20would%20feel%20bored.%20That's%20not%20a%20value%20judgment.%20I%20just%20know%20their%20choice%20isn't%20right%20for%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%2C%20Kate%2C%20retired%20at%2057%20after%20working%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-from-elementary-teacher-how-to-prepare-kids-for-school-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eelementary%20school%20teacher%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Luckily%2C%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20her%20retirement%20lifestyle%20and%20my%20work%20demands.%20I%20make%20sure%20I'm%20available%20during%20the%20evenings%2C%20and%20we%20go%20for%20long%20walks%20on%20the%20weekends.%20We%20travel%20together%20at%20least%20four%20times%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226049b532-674f-4a4c-bee5-ef9dc93db8ae%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20focus%20on%20the%20parts%20of%20work%20that%20bring%20me%20joy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-running-business-tips-work-life-balance-find-time-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20own%20my%20own%20business%3C%2F