%2C%20something%20that%20many%20people%20do%20in%20retirement.%20I%20typically%20work%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20(full%20time%20during%20the%20weekdays%20and%20half%20days%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday).%20Yet%2C%20I%20also%20take%20lots%20of%20time%20away.%20I%20was%20in%20Greece%20for%20my%20daughter's%20wedding%20in%20August%20and%20will%20travel%20to%20Canada%20for%20a%20month%20this%20fall.%20When%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20I'm%20entirely%20unplugged%2C%20able%20to%20join%20Kate%20in%20her%20retirement%20mindset.%20I%20know%20my%20team%20will%20call%20me%20if%20there's%20anything%20truly%20critical.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227536b96c-1d44-48db-9036-36cdc476de59%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20still%20save%20for%20retirement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20plan%20to%20keep%20working%20for%20at%20least%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20I'm%20also%20saving%20for%20my%20old%20age.%20I%20live%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20retirement%20savings%20account%20similar%20to%20a%20401(k)%20that's%20worth%20roughly%20%24700%2C000.%20I%20also%20have%20other%20investments%20that%20are%20more%20risky%20but%20with%20potentially%20higher%20payoffs.%20Eventually%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20live%20off%20the%20return%20from%20my%20investments%2C%20with%20any%20business%20income%20as%20an%20added%20bonus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20plan%20to%20work%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20forever.%20I'm%20crafting%20a%20career%20that%20reflects%20what%20I%20want%20as%20I%20age%3A%20intellectual%20engagement%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20time%20for%20family%20and%20travel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-have-retirement-plans-want-a-career-for-life-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726654023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48d09d17aa3c7b2b2