%20closer%20to%20the%20front%20lines%20where%20it%20most%20impacts%20customers%20(and%20the%20business)%2C%20decrease%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20strengthen%20our%20organizations'%20ability%20to%20make%20customers'%20lives%20better%20and%20easier%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20bet%20that%20somewhere%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20nodded%20his%20head%20when%20he%20heard%20the%20news%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20he's%20been%20speaking%20out%20in%20favor%20of%20flattening%20org%20charts%20both%20publicly%20and%20in%20private%20for%20a%20while%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20want%20a%20management%20structure%20that's%20just%20managers%20managing%20managers%2C%20managing%20managers%2C%20managing%20managers%2C%20managing%20the%20people%20who%20are%20doing%20the%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-might-cut-metas-middle-management-report-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%20reportedly%20said%20in%20an%20internal%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-facebook-new-era-efficiency-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20month%20later%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bworking%20on%20flattening%20our%20org%20structure%20and%20removing%20some%20layers%20of%20middle%20management%20to%20make%20decisions%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-efficiency-facebook-apple-amazon-earnings-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZuckerberg%20also%20proclaimed%20a%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Meta%20last%20year%2C%20following%20two%20rounds%20of%20layoffs%20that%20cumulatively%20cost%20roughly%2021%