atimes.com%2Findia%2Fone-nation-one-election-cleared-by-union-cabinet%2Farticleshow%2F113453377.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%20news%20updates%3A%20Union%20Cabinet%20approves%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20proposal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726651493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F10%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1725945067-7271.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-arvind-kejriwal-pm-modi-us-donald-trump-hezbollah-pager-rg-kar-kolkata-case-israel-124091800145_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latest%20news%20updates%3A%20Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20news%20developments%20from%20across%20the%20world%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-arvind-kejriwal-pm-modi-us-donald-trump-hezbollah-pager-rg-kar-kolkata-case-israel-124091800145_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-arvind-kejriwal-pm-modi-us-donald-trump-hezbollah-pager-rg-kar-kolkata-case-israel-124091800145_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-arvind-kejriwal-pm-modi-us-donald-trump-hezbollah-pager-rg-kar-kolkata-case-israel-124091800145_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%20%7C%20Rahul's%20Rhetoric%20Dents%20India's%20Global%20Image%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20politics%20has%20reached%20a%20critical%20juncture%2C%20where%20finding%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20current%20turmoil%20seems%20elusive.%20While%20dissent%20and%20disagreements%20are%20inherent%20to%20political%20discourse%2C%20they%20should%20not%20translate%20into%20anti-national%20activities.%20Ideological%20conflicts%20are%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20politics%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20should%20lead%20to%20constructive%20criticism%20aimed%20at%20improving%20public%20welfare%20policies%20rather%20than%20being%20driven%20solely%20by%20a%20quest%20for%20power.%20However%2C%20the%20current%20political%20climate%20does%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20India.%20Since%20the%20general%20election%20results%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20opposition%20has%20increased%2C%20but%20it%20is%20troubling%20to%20note%20that%20the%20opposition's%20significance%20appears%20to%20be%20diminishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20democratic%20country%20like%20India%2C%20a%20strong%20opposition%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20a%20positive%20force.%20Yet%2C%20when%20ideological%20differences%20devolve%20into%20hate%20politics%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20serious%20concern.%20Today's%20opposition%20seems%20so%20disoriented%20that%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20abandon%20truth%20and%20national%20security%20in%20favour%20of%20political%20gains.%20This%20was%20evident%20when%20opposition%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20often%20criticized%20for%20his%20short-sightedness%2C%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20present%20a%20distorted%20image%20of%20India%20overseas.%20His%20remarks%2C%20which%20frequently%20criticize%20India's%20unity%20and%20diversity%2C%20reflect%20a%20troubling%20trend.%20At%20times%2C%20he%20portrays%20Hindus%20as%20violent%20or%20intolerant%2C%20while%20other%20times%2C%20he%20aligns%20with%20Western%20perspectives%20to%20undermine%20Indian%20culture%20and%20the%20freedoms%20of%20Indian%20women%2C%20calling%20them%20myths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20failed%20to%20mention%20to%20his%20American%20audience%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20actively%20promoted%20women's%20rights.%20Instead%2C%20he%20questioned%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20BJP%20manipulated%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20and%20claiming%20that%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20were%20hacked%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20results%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20the%20EC%20had%20been%20non-partisan.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20these%20claims%20undermine%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20Such%20statements%20could%20be%20music%20to%20the%20ears%20of%20nations%20like%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20which%20have%20little%20regard%20for%20Indian%20interests%20and%20could%20use%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20further%20their%20own%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20dishonest%20and%20detrimental%20to%20highlight%20India's%20alleged%20problems%20with%20exaggerations%20and%20falsehoods%20to%20score%20political%20points%20and%20present%20oneself%20favourably%20abroad.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20underlying%20motives%3A%20Is%20this%20meant%20to%20portray%20India%20as%20a%20fractured%20nation%20and%20a%20dysfunctional%20democracy%2C%20thereby%20inviting%20foreign%20intervention%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20concerning%20are%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20comments%20regarding%20Sikhs.%20During%20his%20time%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20the%20core%20issue%20in%20India%20was%20whether%20Sikhs%20could%20wear%20a%20turban%2C%20carry%20a%20kada%2C%20or%20visit%20a%20gurdwara.%20His%20frequent%20criticism%20of%20India%20during%20his%20foreign%20travels%2C%20including%20engaging%20with%20individuals%20associated%20with%20an%20anti-India%20agenda%2C%20is%20highly%20objectionable.%20Notably%2C%20figures%20like%20Ilhan%20Omar%2C%20who%20have%20criticized%20Kashmir's%20status%2C%20align%20with%20the%20INC%20and%20Rahul's%20political%20stances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20sponsored%20by%20Friends%20of%20Democracy%20(an%20organization%20linked%20to%20George%20Soros)%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Modi%20Mirage%3A%20New%20Study%20Indicates%20a%20Decline%20in%20India's%20Global%20Reputation%20under%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20released%20on%20May%206%2C%202024%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20Indian%20elections.%20This%20report%2C%20curated%20by%20Professor%20Irfan%20Nooruddin%20of%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20Dr.%20Subir%20Sinha%20of%20London%20University%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Ritumbra%20Manuvie%20of%20Groningen%20University%2C%20synthesizes%20research%20from%20sources%20like%20Pew%20Research%20Centre%2C%20V-Dem%2C%20and%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace.%20These%20sources%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20anti-India%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20portrayal%20of%20India%20as%20a%20caste-obsessed%20society%20where%20people%20cannot%20freely%20practice%20their%20faith%20and%20where%20certain%20groups%20are%20unsafe%20is%20erroneous%20and%20misleading.%20His%20statements%2C%20which%20reflect%20the%20views%20of%20social%20media%20influencers%20from%20specific%20castes%20and%20those%20advocating%20for%20a%20separate%20Kashmir%2C%20undermine%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%20Such%20objectionable%20rhetoric%20from%20the%20INC%20only%20serves%20to%20harm%20India's%20global%20standing%20and%20its%20internal%20cohesion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20believes%20that%20affirmative%20action%20will%20revive%20the%20Congress%20Party%20in%20India.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20the%20country's%20backward%20castes%20and%20communities%20for%20their%20lack%20of%20opportunities.%20His%20remarks%20abroad%20portray%20India%20as%20a%20Brahmin-Baniya%20nexus%20where%20no%20one%20else%20can%20succeed.%20This%20narrative%20is%20misleading%20and%20undermines%20the%20significant%20efforts%20India%20has%20made%20since%20independence%20to%20uplift%20large%20sections%20of%20its%20population%2C%20who%20endured%20centuries%20of%20foreign%20rule.%20Such%20statements%20discredit%20the%20efforts%20of%20his%20party%20to%20offer%20all%20Indians%20a%20fair%20chance%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20Gandhi%20family's%20long%20history%20of%20leadership%20in%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20falsely%20accuses%20the%20RSS%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20of%20devaluing%20certain%20Indian%20languages%20and%20cultures.%20He%20claims%20that%20the%20RSS%20and%20its%20affiliates%20view%20Tamil%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Manipuri%2C%20and%20Bengali%20as%20inferior.%20However%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20overlooks%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20efforts%20to%20celebrate%20India's%20diverse%20languages%20and%20traditions.%20For%20instance%2C%20Modi%20has%20repeatedly%20hailed%20Tamil%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20languages%20and%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20promises%20to%20promote%20Tamil%20globally.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20initiated%20the%20annual%20Kashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam%2C%20a%20month-long%20celebration%20highlighting%20the%20ancient%20ties%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Varanasi%2C%20aiming%20to%20bridge%20the%20north-south%20divide%20that%20has%20been%20politically%20manipulated%20by%20some%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20UNCIRF%20(UN%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom)%20report%2C%20which%20labels%20India%20as%20a%20'country%20of%20particular%20concern%2C'%20seems%20to%20reflect%20a%20coordinated%20and%20biased%20narrative%20aimed%20at%20undermining%20India's%20rising%20status%20as%20a%20global%20power.%20Such%20interventions%2C%20often%20misguided%2C%20raise%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20understanding%20of%20India's%20cultural%20fabric%20and%20reflect%20the%20biases%20of%20those%20behind%20them.%20The%20campaign%20against%20India%20abroad%20involves%20various%20fronts%20with%20lofty%20names%20but%20similar%20motives%2C%20all%20working%20to%20tarnish%20India's%20global%20image.%20Reports%20by%20organizations%20like%20V-Dem%2C%20which%20are%20perceived%20to%20have%20a%20colonial%20bias%2C%20circulate%20in%20India's%20political%20discourse%2C%20often%20targeting%20the%20Modi%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20poised%20for%20significant%20progress%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20and%20resurgent%20India%20is%20not%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20many%20global%20powers.%20The%20year%202024%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Indian%20history%2C%20marked%20by%20attempts%20to%20erode%20nationalistic%20sentiments%20through%20slanted%20narratives%20aimed%20at%20dividing%20society.%20Despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20India%20continues%20to%20advance%20towards%20its%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%20Viksit%20Bharat%20by%202047.%20The%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20INDI%20Alliance%2C%20which%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20derisively%20mocked%2C%20have%20adopted%20divisive%20narratives%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20leaders.%20This%20stance%20is%20particularly%20intriguing%20given%20India's%20commitment%20to%20pluralism%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20approach%2C%20driven%20by%20divisive%20and%20appeasement%20politics%2C%20ultimately%20harms%20both%20the%20Hindu%20community%20and%20the%20nation.%20A%20leadership%20that%20represents%20all%20Indians%2C%20rather%20than%20specific%20communities%2C%20is%20essential.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20reveal%20political%20immaturity%20and%20an%20anti-national%20agenda.%20His%20statements%20on%20global%20platforms%20seem%20more%20focused%20on%20scoring%20political%20points%20rather%20than%20fostering%20constructive%20dialogue.%20His%20actions%20raise%20doubts%20about%20whether%20he%20aims%20to%20promote%20or%20tarnish%20India's%20image%20for%20personal%20gain.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20oppose%20such%20divisive%20politics%20to%20protect%20India's%20democracy%20and%20cultural%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Rajiv%20Tuli%20is%20a%20columnist%20and%20commentator%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Barthwal%20teaches%20Political%20Science%20at%20Sri%20Aurobindo%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726651380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22