%20her.%20Her%20mental%20health%20deteriorated-she%20started%20self-harming%2C%20became%20depressed%2C%20and%20suicidal%20to%20the%20point%20where%20she%20stopped%20eating.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanda%20pleads%20with%20the%20UK%20Government%20to%20pass%20a%20law%20to%20help%20parents%20%26quot%3Bbring%20their%20children%20back%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Continental%20Epidemic%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Amanda%2C%20millions%20of%20parents%20across%20Europe%20are%20increasingly%20vocal%20about%20the%20damaging%20effects%20of%20smartphones%20on%20their%20children.%20Parent-led%20movements%20are%20pushing%20for%20stricter%20screen%20time%20regulations%2C%20and%20even%20bans%20in%20schools%2C%20calling%20for%20comprehensive%20policies%20to%20protect%20the%20next%20generation's%20future.%20More%20than%2010%2C000%20mothers%20with%20young%20children%20in%20Spain%20have%20created%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20to%20inform%20one%20another%20of%20the%20state%20of%20their%20children's%20mental%20health%20and%20exchange%20tips%20on%20dealing%20with%20smartphone%20addiction.%20They%20want%20help%20from%20their%20government%20and%20demand%20legislation%20to%20ban%20smartphone%20use%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20growing%20concern%20has%20sparked%20intense%20debates%20across%20Europe%20about%20how%20to%20address%20screen%20addiction%20among%20children.%20Movements%20advocating%20for%20phone-free%20schools%20are%20gaining%20momentum.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20legislation%2C%20some%20schools%20have%20started%20implementing%20smartphone-free%20classes%20and%20some%20others%20have%20completely%20banned%20phones%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Crisis%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20smartphone%20market%20has%20exploded%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20no%20signs%20of%20slowing%20down.%20The%20youth%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20spend%20countless%20hours%20on%20their%20devices.%20Deloitte%20predicts%20that%20by%202026%2C%20India%20will%20be%20the%20second-largest%20smartphone%20market%2C%20surpassing%20one%20billion%20users%2C%20with%20rural%20areas%20driving%20sales%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndian%20youth%20are%20consumed%20by%20social%20media%20and%20smartphones%2C%20which%20have%20been%20linked%20to%20mental%20health%20problems%20like%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20social%20isolation.%20A%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20(BCG)%20study%20reveals%20that%20half%20of%20Indian%20consumers%20pick%20up%20their%20phones%20out%20of%20habit%2C%20often%20without%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20India%20warn%20that%20more%20comprehensive%20studies%20are%20needed%20to%20understand%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20smartphones%20on%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20both%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20set%20up%20de-addiction%20and%20research%20centres%20focused%20on%20phone%20addiction.%20While%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20taken%20steps%20to%20encourage%20responsible%20usage%2C%20more%20action%20is%20needed.%20In%202015%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20introduced%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Addiction%20of%20Technological%20Gadgets%20Bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20but%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20it%20was%20ever%20passed%20into%20law.%3Cbr%3E%5CnCan%20we%20expect%20teenagers%20to%20resist%20what%20adults%20cannot%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20millions%20of%20others%2C%20I%20rely%20on%20my%20smartphone%20for%20nearly%20every%20aspect%20of%20life-reading%2C%20writing%2C%20social%20media%2C%20internet%20browsing%2C%20and%20communication.%20I%20use%20it%20for%20payments%2C%20watching%20TV%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20music.%20With%20multiple%20OTT%20subscriptions%2C%20I%20have%20more%20content%20at%20my%20fingertips%20than%20I%20could%20ever%20use.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSo%2C%20is%20it%20fair%20to%20expect%20teenagers%20to%20limit%20their%20screen%20time%20and%20curb%20their%20dependence%20on%20smartphones%3F%20Some%20experts%20argue%20that%20banning%20smartphones%20in%20schools%20is%20ineffective%20and%20anti-technology.%20Instead%2C%20they%20believe%20students%20should%20be%20educated%20on%20responsible%20usage.%20Others%20warn%20that%20a%20ban%20might%20lead%20to%20covert%20smartphone%20use%20or%20smuggling%20of%20devices%20into%20classrooms.%20The%20focus%2C%20they%20say%2C%20should%20be%20on%20teaching%20children%20the%20benefits%20of%20responsible%20use%20and%20the%20dangers%20of%20overuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Scale%20Of%20The%20Problem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Miller%20believes%20smartphones%20are%20%26quot%3Bkilling%20our%20children%2C%20killing%20their%20youth%2C%20destroying%20their%20mental%20health%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20UK's%20broadcasting%20and%20telecommunications%20regulatory%20authority%2C%20Ofcom%2C%20%26quot%3Bby%20the%20age%20of%2012%2C%2097%25%20of%20children%20have%20their%20own%20mobile%20phones%26quot%3B.%20Studies%20have%20shown%20that%20increased%20screen%20time%20negatively%20impacts%20mental%20health%2C%20academic%20performance%2C%20and%20social%20skills.%20Adolescents%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20anxiety%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20sleep%20problems%20due%20to%20excessive%20smartphone%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20as%20much%20as%2068%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20used%20smartphones%2C%20and%20over%2060%25%20of%20people%20in%20many%20countries%20admitted%20to%20being%20addicted%20to%20their%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmartphones%20have%20fuelled%20the%20rise%20of%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20allowing%20celebrities%20to%20connect%20with%20their%20young%20fans.%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20reached%20one%20billion%20followers%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%20in%20September%2C%20with%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20his%20fanbase%20being%20young%20adults.%20Other%20youth%20icons%2C%20such%20as%20Selena%20Gomez%2C%20Justin%20Bieber%2C%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20also%20have%20millions%20of%20followers%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20hold%20smartphones%20have%20over%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20smartphones%20offer%20practical%20benefits%20like%20communication%20and%20education%2C%20those%20opposing%20a%20ban%20argue%20that%20implementing%20it%20could%20brand%20Europe%20as%20anti-technology.%20However%2C%20the%20device's%20addictive%20nature%2C%20similar%20to%20gaming%20addiction%2C%20raises%20concerns.%20Last%20year%2C%20UNESCO%20called%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20smartphones%20in%20schools%2C%20and%20France%20has%20already%20enforced%20one.%20The%20UK%20is%20seriously%20considering%20banning%20smartphones%20for%20children%20aged%20five%20to%2016%20in%20schools%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20guidelines%20issued%20earlier%20this%20year%20supporting%20head%20teachers%20who%20prohibit%20mobile%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20British%20schools%20have%20already%20banned%20smartphones%20with%20great%20success%2C%20seeing%20improvements%20in%20academic%20performance%20and%20reduced%20distractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Experiment%20That%20Gives%20Hope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%2010%20teenagers%20from%20a%20Manchester%20school%20participated%20in%20a%20five-day%20experiment%2C%20swapping%20their%20smartphones%20for%20basic%20mobile%20phones%20that%20only%20allowed%20calls%20and%20texts.%20These%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20aged%2014%20to%2016%2C%20previously%20spent%20over%2012%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20their%20devices.%20While%20one%20participant%20demanded%20his%20smartphone%20back%2C%20the%20other%20nine%20completed%20the%20experiment.%20One%20boy%20reported%20better%20sleep%20and%20another%20girl%20shared%20that%20her%20relationship%20with%20her%20father%20improved%20as%20they%20spent%20more%20time%20talking.%20Though%20a%20small%20sample%2C%20the%20experiment%20suggested%20that%20life%20without%20smartphones%20is%20possible%20for%20even%20the%20most%20dependent%20teens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20British%20government%20contemplates%20the%20ban%20a%20school%20trust%20in%20England%20with%2035%2C000%20pupils%20has%20just%20announced%20it%20is%20banning%20smartphones%20in%20all%20its%2042%20schools%20in%20England.%20The%20trust%20hopes%20that%20the%20ban%20will%20lead%20to%20higher%20academic%20achievement%20and%20improve%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20its%20pupils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726649700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-07%2Fmobile-phone_650x400_81501483347.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-a-smartphone-epidemic-is-destroying-europes-new-generation-6592345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parent-led%20movements%20are%20pushing%20for%20stricter%20screen%20time%20regulations%2C%20and%20even%20bans%20in%20schools%2C%20calling%20for%20comprehensive%20policies%20to%20protect%20the%20next%20generation's%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-a-smartphone-epidemic-is-destroying-europes-new-generation-6592345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italy's%20World%20Cup%20icon%20Schillaci%20dies%20aged%2059%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726649684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_sport%2Feb7a%2Flive%2F5c0f70d0-6139-11ee-ac8c-9d18dbc280ea.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcqlvrp4nylwo%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Italian%20World%20Cup%20icon%20Salvatore%20Schillaci%2C%20the%20top%20scorer%20at%20the%201990%20World%20Cup%2C%20dies%20aged%2059.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2854%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcqlvrp4nylwo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcqlvrp4nylwo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fcqlvrp4nylwo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGirls%20Out%20Of%20Class%2012...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Wants%20Cops%20At%20Bengal%20Medical%20Colleges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20faced%20tough%20questions%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20steps%20it%20has%20taken%20to%20beef%20up%20security%20in%20the%20state's%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20horrific%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%20listed%20the%20state%20government's%20steps%20to%20step%20up%20security%20at%20hospitals%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20questioned%20why%20contractual%20staff%2C%20and%20not%20regular%20cops%2C%20were%20on%20security%20duty%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20doctor's%20rape-murder%2C%20was%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20who%20had%20unfettered%20access%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20if%20the%20new%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20the%20hospitals%20were%20regular%20cops%20or%20contractual%20staff%20under%20the%20state%20government's%20Rattirer%20Sathi%20(night%20companion)%20programme%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20healthcare%20staff.%20Mr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20they%20were%20cops%2C%20and%20clarified%20that%20contractual%20staff%20on%20security%20duty%20was%20a%20short-term%20measure%20and%20would%20be%20replaced%20by%20regular%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20Mr%20Sibal%2C%20what%20really%20happened%20was%20this.%20The%20accused%20was%20drawn%20from%20the%20volunteer%20force.%20If%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20another%20set%20of%20contractual%20people...%20these%20contractual%20people%20will%20be%20trained%20for%20seven%20days%20and%20then%20they%20will%20be%20walking%20all%20around%20in%20the%20hospital.%20What%20is%20the%20protection%20young%20doctors%20have%2C%20particularly%20the%20women%20doctors%2C%20with%20these%20contractual%20staff%20walking%20around%20at%20night%20in%20the%20hospital%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20these%20security%20personnel%20would%20be%20deployed%20in%20addition%20to%20regular%20cops%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20face%20it%2C%20the%20crime%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20volunteer%20who%20is%20posted%20at%20the%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20then%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20deployed%20at%20hospitals%20now%20are%20not%20civic%20volunteers%2C%20but%20from%20a%20security%20agency%20the%20state%20government%20has%20hired%20and%20proper%20verification%20is%20done%20before%20they%20are%20recruited.%20The%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20if%20these%20personnel%20were%20undergoing%20psychological%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20doctors%20have%20a%20feeling%20of%20insecurity.%20They%20don't%20know%20who%20these%20people%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20replied%20that%20CISF%20personnel%20are%20currently%20deployed%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20the%20junior%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20on%20a%20'cease%20work'%20protest%20can%20join%20duty.%20%26quot%3BCISF%20will%20be%20there%20for%20a%20short%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied.%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20the%20state%20government%20will%20make%20arrangements%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20doctors%20pressed%20that%20they%20want%20regular%20cops%20on%20duty%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20told%20the%20state%20government%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20problem%20when%20you%20entrust%20security%20to%20contractual%20staff%2C%20particularly%20in%20hospitals%2C%20where%20people%20are%20on%20duty%20for%2036%20hours%2C%20there%20is%20virtually%20no%20protection%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20there%20is%20a%20police%20outpost%20in%20every%20hospital%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNotwithstanding%20a%20police%20outpost%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20delayed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sibal%20responded%20that%20the%20state%20government%20would%20disband%20Rattirer%20Sathi%20if%20the%20court%20wanted%20that%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20the%20court%20wanting%20it%2C%20we%20are%20not%20in%20charge%20of%20governance.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20the%20court%20must%20have%20some%20confidence%20in%20the%20state%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20young%20students%20come%20to%20government%20medical%20colleges%20to%20pursue%20medicine.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20young%20girls%20straight%20of%2012th%20standard%20who%20are%20going%20to%20be%20there%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20dealing%20with%20young%20people%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-23%20years.%20They%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20protected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20in%20the%2045%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%2C%20regular%20cops%20must%20be%20on%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20have%20%26quot%3Bno%20great%20pleasure%20in%20abstaining%20from%20work%26quot%3B.%20They%20are%20abstaining%20because%20with%20these%20contractual%20people%2C%20they%20have%20a%20new%20source%20of%20insecurity%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20devil%20lies%20in%20the%20fine%20print.%20You%20say%20you%20will%20sanction%20funds%2C%20duty%20rooms%20are%20being%20constructed...%20the%20collector%2C%20district%20magistrate%20and%20police%20superintendent%20must%20oversee%20that%20these%20(security)%20arrangements%20are%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20SOP%20must%20be%20followed%20to%20identify%20locations%20for%20CCTVs.%20%26quot%3BThey%20must%20cover%20areas%20where%20female%20doctors%20rest%2C%20the%20bathrooms%20they%20use%20because%20these%20are%20areas%20where%20they%20are%20vulnerable.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20they%20have%20an%20SOP%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20doctors%20protesting%20against%20the%20August%209%20incident%20and%20demanding%20security%20at%20work%20have%20welcomed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20and%20said%20they%20have%20been%20against%20putting%20volunteers%20with%20seven-day%20training%20on%20security%20duty.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20this%20security%20arrangement%20that%20relies%20on%20contractual%20staff%20is%20not%20suitable%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20West%20Bengal%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Front%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContractual%20Security%20Staff%20Under%20Scanner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20August%209%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20as%20the%20main%20accused%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20this%20workforce.%20An%20initiative%20started%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20after%20she%20came%20to%20power%2C%20civic%20volunteers%20were%20roped%20in%20to%20assist%20regular%20cops.%20According%20to%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%201.19%20lakh%20civic%20volunteers%20in%20Bengal%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criteria%20to%20be%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20are%20simple%20--%20the%20candidate%20must%20have%20studied%20till%20Class%20VIII%2C%20be%20medically%20fit%20and%20not%20have%20a%20criminal%20record.%20There%20are%20no%20written%20tests%20and%20the%20Opposition%20alleges%20that%20proximity%20to%20Trinamool%20leaders%20is%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjoy%20Roy%2C%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20RG%20Kar%20case%2C%20was%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20but%20enjoyed%20access%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20state-run%20hospital%20round%20the%20clock.%20He%20roamed%20about%20in%20a%20bike%20with%20a%20'Kolkata%20Police'%20sticker%2C%20wore%20a%20'Kolkata%20Police'%20t-shirt%20and%20often%20stayed%20at%20police%20barracks%20--%20all%20this%20despite%20not%20being%20a%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipak%20Burman%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Falakata%2C%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20that%20civic%20volunteers%20are%20recruited%20only%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20inspectors-in-charge%20and%20sub-inspectors%20move%20around%20with%20three%20to%20five%20civic%20police%20these%20days.%20Their%20jobs%20are%20to%20run%20personal%20errands%20for%20the%20cops%2C%20extort%20money%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20run%20surveillance%20on%20Opposition%20politicians.%20And%20whenever%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20addresses%20a%20public%20meeting%20or%20attends%20a%20government%20programme%20in%20the%20districts%2C%20they%20discard%20the%20uniform%20and%20turn%20up%20as%20Trinamool%20supporters%20to%20fill%20the%20venue%20cheering%20loudly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20written%20tests%2C%20there%20are%20no%20interviews.%20Who%20decides%20who%20is%20fit%20to%20be%20a%20civic%20volunteer%3F%20The%20ruling%20party%20provides%20a%20list%20and%20the%20recruitments%20take%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20CPM%20leader%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20told%20The%20Telegraph.%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20the%20civic%20police%20are%20controlling%20the%20police%20because%20of%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20political%20bosses.%20The%20policing%20system%20has%20been%20completely%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726648860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbha0531o_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_18_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-devil-lies-in-fine-print-chief-justice-grills-bengal-on-doctors-safety-6592221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20faced%20tough%20questions%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20steps%20it%20has%20taken%20to%20beef%20up%20security%20in%20the%20state's%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20horrific%20rape-murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-devil-lies-in-fine-print-chief-justice-grills-bengal-on-doctors-safety-6592221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20town%20hall%20event%20in%20Michigan%3A%20Here%20are%20the%20key%20takeaways%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726648807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113456671%2Cimgsize-780860.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrumps-town-hall-event-in-michigan-here-are-the-key-takeaways%2Farticleshow%2F113448804.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5