all%20centres%20in%20Delhi%20-%20said%20he%20got%20a%20call%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ffrom-azamgarh-to-us-to-yamunapar-deadly-games-of-5-big-gangsters-6577686%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20aides%2C%20who%20tried%20to%20extort%20Rs%2010%20crore%20from%20him.%20He%20said%20he%20also%20received%20extortion%20calls%20from%20Canada-based%20terrorist%20Goldy%20Brar.%C2%A0Chhabra%20denied%20that%20he%20runs%C2%A0call%20centres%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20owns%20an%20event%20management%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhabra%20had%20then%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Bishnoi%20in%20June%202023%2C%20which%20had%20irked%20the%20gangster.%20Around%20this%20time%2C%20Bishnoi%20was%20taken%20into%20police%20custody%20and%20allegedly%20tortured%20and%20he%20held%20Chhabra%20and%20Shah%20responsible%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20call%20five%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Bishnoi%20told%20him%20that%20now%20he%20doesn't%20want%20money%20but%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20Rs%2010%20crore%20now%2C%20I%20want%20you%20dead.%20Get%20your%20bier%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhabra%20also%20said%20that%20his%20gang%20members%20told%20him%20that%20they%20knew%20everything%20about%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20where%20my%20brother%20works%20to%20what%20I%20do%2C%20they%20said%20they%20know%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20recordings%2C%20which%20I%20had%20shared%20with%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20when%20he%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20them%2C%20they%20told%20him%20that%20all%20this%20would%20be%20kept%20discreet%20and%20that%20he%20would%20be%20given%20police%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20happened%20for%20a%20year%20and%20then%20they%20took%20away%20my%