r%20aspects%20of%20photography%20%E2%80%94%20framing%2C%20angles%2C%20camera%20settings%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20had%20already%20visited%2010%20national%20parks%20and%20Masai%20Mara%2C%20spending%2030%20to%2040%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20wild%20on%20safaris%20and%20expeditions.%20For%20a%20young%20child%2C%20navigating%20the%20outdoors%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20easy%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20walking%20required%2C%20but%20Shreyovi%20embraced%20the%20challenge%20with%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShreyovi%20is%20quite%20hardy%20and%20resilient.%20She%20accompanies%20us%20on%20small%20hikes%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20never%20shies%20away%20from%20rough%20terrains.%20She%20is%20very%20disciplined%20and%20is%20up%20early%20daily%20to%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20proud%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20age%20of%20eight%2C%20Shreyovi%20has%20been%20waking%20up%20at%204%3A30%20am%20to%20practice%20her%20photography%20skills%20before%20school.%20She%20joins%20her%20mentors%20from%20Nature%20Wanderers%20every%20morning%20from%205%20to%206%20am%2C%20learning%20and%20refining%20her%20craft.%20This%20routine%20has%20instilled%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20discipline%20in%20her.%20On%20weekends%2C%20her%20parents%20take%20her%20to%20wetlands%20or%20nearby%20open%20spaces%20in%20Faridabad%20to%20further%20nurture%20her%20passion%20for%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%2C%20Shiv%20Nadar%20School%2C%20has%20also%20been%20highly%20supportive%20of%20her%20pursuits%2C%20say%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoughing%20it%20out%20for%20the%20perfect%20click!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Shreyovi%20visited%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20where%20she%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20photography%20exhibition%20and%20was%20mesmerised%20by%20the%20breathtaking%20images%20on%20display%2C%20solidifying%20her%20own%20aspiration