16641%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-the-assassination-attempt-on-donald-trump-is-affecting-us-election-bets-and-polls-13216641%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhow-the-assassination-attempt-on-donald-trump-is-affecting-us-election-bets-and-polls-13216641%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Dhabas%20To%20Save%20on%20Your%20Maps%20for%20the%20Next%20Road%20Trip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20distinctly%20recall%20a%202019%20college%20road%20trip%20to%20Kasara%20which%20lies%20along%20the%20Mumbai-Nashik%20route.%20The%20plan%20was%20an%20overnight%20trek%20to%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sandhan%20Valley%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Valley%20of%20Shadows).%20We%20decided%20to%20fuel%20up%20before%20commencing%20the%20long%20walk%20through%20the%20ravine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20local%20food%20joint%2C%20piping%20hot%20Maggi%2C%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20savoury%20Indian%20pastry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pavs%3C%2Fem%3E%20(deep%20fried%20potato%20dumplings%20in%20bread)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoccupied%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20ricketty%20table%20as%2017%20hungry%20adolescents%20feasted%20to%20their%20heart%E2%80%99s%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManners%20and%20etiquette%20waltzed%20out%20through%20the%20window%20as%20we%20smacked%20our%20lips%20and%20licked%20the%20spicy%20Maharashtrian%20garlic%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoff%20our%20fingers.%20It%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20why%20since%20time%20immemorial%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360331%2Fnational-highway-restaurants-food-joints-expressway-karnal-haveli-amrik-sukhdev-azad-hind-dhaba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(roadside%20food%20stalls)%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20truck%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresumab