5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplay%20with%20other%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereminded%20us%20that%20some%20experiences%20are%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20enjoying%20some%20hot%20Maggi%20and%20tea%20near%20the%20waterfall%2C%20we%20started%20our%20return%20journey%2C%20only%20to%20be%20greeted%20by%20a%20herd%20of%20cows%20and%20buffaloes.%20Our%20son%20was%20completely%20captivated%2C%20sitting%20and%20watching%20them%20for%20several%20minutes.%20We%20eventually%20had%20to%20coax%20him%20away%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20bring%20him%20back!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20returned%20home%20that%20evening%2C%20our%20hearts%20full%20and%20our%20pockets%20brimming%20with%20unforgettable%20memories%2C%20realising%20what%20we%20had%20been%20missing%20all%20along.%20Our%20son%20had%20made%20new%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20hens%2C%20cows%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20swans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20simple%20moments%20made%20the%20day%20truly%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20digital%20world%20where%20children%20are%20often%20glued%20to%20screens%2C%20introducing%20them%20to%20nature%20has%20never%20been%20more%20important.%20Nehal%20Shah%20realised%20this%20after%20becoming%20a%20mother.%20As%20an%20avid%20trekker%2C%20she%20sought%20out%20places%20and%20trips%20suitable%20for%20her%20infant%2C%20but%20her%20searches%20only%20led%20to%20indoor%20activities.%20Frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20outdoor%20options%20for%20young%20children%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20create%20something%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nehal%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3