g%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tocco%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20pack%20this%20childhood%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20box%20for%20other%20people%20to%20enjoy.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20onboarding%20the%20first%20two%20chefs%2C%20Reshma%20brought%20in%20more%2C%20expanding%20the%20platform%20to%20include%20over%2016%20chefs%20from%20different%20cities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20They%20offer%20snacks%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20jackfruit%20chips%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshankarpali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sweet%20snack)%3Cem%3E%2C%20masalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20sambar%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20podi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powder)%2C%20pickles%20like%20prawn%2C%20cut%20mango%2C%20homemade%20curd%20chilli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuli%20inji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ginger%20pickle)%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2058-year-old%20Uma%20Suresh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20cooking%20since%20she%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20Tocco%20has%20given%20new%20meaning%20to%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CCooking%20is%20my%20passion.%20I%20would%20always%20pack%20some%20pickles%20for%20anyone%20who%20came%20home.%20I%20always%20dreamed%20of%20running%20a%20business%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20daughters%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20made%20a%20name%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%