ss%20story%20is%20written%20by%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESquare-shaped%20pieces%20of%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20visited%20Kozhikode%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20sacrilege%20to%20not%20return%20home%20with%20servings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20also%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%98prestige%20symbol%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20has%20an%20interesting%20story%20that%20prequels%20its%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20supposedly%20an%20Arab%20invention%20born%20around%20the%2016th%20century%20when%20the%20community%20settled%20in%20Kerala.%20They%20were%20intent%20on%20gifting%20a%20piece%20of%20their%20culinary%20prowess%20to%20Kozhikode%E2%80%99s%20Zamorin%20(monarch).%20And%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20the%20cut.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20spice%20trade%20and%20eventually%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20been%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20a%20simple%20blend%20of%20water%2C%20sugar%2C%20corn%20starch%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20citrus%20salt%2C%20and%20flavourings%20birthed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281110%2Fmithai-map-of-india-10-lesser-known-indian-sweets-you-must-try-at-least-once%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dessert%20so%20exquisite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20successor%20dessert%20could%20compete%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20no%20two%20blocks%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20same%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20each%20ingredient%20varies%20from%20proprietor%20to%20proprietor%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20tourists%20and%20locals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20picky%20about%20these%20changing%20nuances%20so%20long%20as%20they